n%20a%20state%20BJP%20chief%2C%20a%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%2C%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20national%20working%20committee.%20The%20man%20replacing%20Shivraj%20Sing%20Chouhan%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20is%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20and%20former%20minister%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20will%20have%20two%20deputies%20--%20%26quot%3BPeople's%20princess%26quot%3B%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20who%20was%20an%20aspirant%20for%20the%20top%20post%20--%20and%20senior%20leader%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20longest%20serving%20party-men%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20could%20not%20be%20more%20different%20from%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20who%20helmed%20state%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20party%20for%20three%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2056-year-old%2C%20initially%20associated%20with%20the%20ABVP%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20party's%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20has%20always%20kept%20a%20low%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20state%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20party%2C%20he%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20organisation%20man%2C%20unlike%20Ms%20Raje%2C%20who%20was%20often%20seen%20to%20be%20at%20variance%20with%20the%20top%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20of%20a%20Brahmin%20face%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20safe%20choice%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20Rajputs%20and%20Jats%20are%20the%20dominant%20castes.%20But%20picking%20a%20member%20from%20either%20community%20carries%20the%20risk%20of%20reverse%20polarisation%20next%20year--%20a%20situation%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20afford.%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20was%20acceptable%20to%20both%20communities%20as%20she%2C%20an%20erstwhile%20royal%2C%20was%20a%20Rajput%20who%20married%20into%20a%20Jat%20family.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20factoring%20in%20caste%20and%20class%20arithmetic%20in%20a%20big%20way%20in%20the%20heartland%20states%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20next%20year's%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20there%20was%20speculation%20that%20Ms%20Raje%2C%20the%20party's%20tallest%20leader%20in%20the%20state%2C%20will%20be%20benched.%20The%20pattern%20is%20similar%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20four-time%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20and%20Chhattisgarh's%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Raman%20Singh%2C%20were%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Shivraj%20Chauhan%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20yesterday%2C%20Ms%20Raje%20was%20the%20one%20to%20propose%20the%20name%20of%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20at%20the%20legislature%20party%20meeting%20this%20afternoon.%20It%20was%20seconded%20by%20state%20leaders%20Kirori%20Meena%2C%20Madan%20Dilawar%20and%20Jawar%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20of%20unity%2C%20though%2C%20has%20only%20drawn%20public%20attention%20to%20the%20senior%20leaders.%20Throughout%20yesterday%2C%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20trended%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20intense%20speculation%20on%20what%20would%20be%20next%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702384380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F8s2fn0b4_bhajanlal-sharma-_625x300_12_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-is-bjps-rajasthan-chief-minister-choice-4659836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20--%20fielding%20fresh%20faces%20for%20the%20top%20jobs%20in%20the%20heartland%20states%20it%20won%20--%20appears%20to%20have%20reserved%20its%20biggest%20surprise%20for%20Rajasthan.%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20is%20a%20first-time%20MLA%20from%20Sanganer%20and%20the%20state%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20party%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-is-bjps-rajasthan-chief-minister-choice-4659836%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-