t%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702384022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105936851%2Cimgsize-19382.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feu-awards-mahsa-amini-rights-prize-as-iran-blocks-family%2Farticleshow%2F105936851.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105936851.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20European%20Parliament%20awarded%20Mahsa%20Amini%2C%20a%20victim%20of%20Iranian%20custody%20who%20sparked%20protests%2C%20with%20the%20EU%20Sakharov%20Prize.%20Amini's%20family%20was%20blocked%20by%20the%20Iranian%20government%20from%20attending%20the%20ceremony.%20This%20recognition%20adds%20to%20the%20international%20acclaim%20received%20by%20women%20challenging%20Iran's%20religious%20government%2C%20following%20Narges%20Mohammadi's%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize.%20The%20refusal%20to%20let%20Amini's%20family%20attend%20has%20outraged%20EU%20lawmakers%2C%20who%20believe%20Tehran%20is%20suppressing%20her%20supporters.%20The%20EU%20has%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20Iranian%20officials%20for%20repressing%20the%20demonstrators.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feu-awards-mahsa-amini-rights-prize-as-iran-blocks-family%2Farticleshow%2F105936851.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feu-awards-mahsa-amini-rights-prize-as-iran-blocks-family%2Famp_articleshow%2F105936851.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feu-awards-mahsa-amini-rights-prize-as-iran-blocks-family%2Famp_articleshow%2F105936851.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20BJP's%20State%20Surprises%20Reveal%20About%20Its%20Succession%20Planning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20observed%20in%20a%202016%20Harvard%20Business%20Review%20paper%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20study%20of%20the%20world's%202%2C500%20largest%20public%20companies%20shows%20that%20companies%20that%20scramble%20to%20find%20replacements%20for%20departing%20CEOs%20forgo%20an%20average%20of%20%241.8%20billion%20in%20shareholder%20value.%20A%20separate%20study%20reveals%20that%20the%20longer%20it%20takes%20a%20company%20to%20name%20a%20new%20CEO%20during%20a%20succession%20crisis%2C%20the%20worse%20it%20subsequently%20performs%20relative%20to%20its%20peers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20holds%20true%20for%20companies%20is%20also%20relevant%20to%20political%20parties.%20A%20poorly%20executed%20succession%20plan%20for%20a%20company%20leads%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20investor%2Fshareholder%20value%2C%20while%20for%20political%20parties%2C%20it%20translates%20into%20shrinking%20support%20base%20and%20electoral%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20concludes%20that%20while%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20perfect%20successor%20is%20yet%20to%20evolve%20fully%2C%20there%20are%20steps%20a%20board%20can%20take%20to%20find%20one%2C%20with%20the%20most%20crucial%20being%20to%20have%20a%20well-thought-out%20plan%20and%20to%20execute%20it%20diligently%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20apply%20the%20findings%20of%20this%20paper%20to%20the%20BJP's%20succession%20planning%20and%20contrast%20it%20with%20the%20Congress'%20approach%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20illustrate%2C%20we%20can%20examine%20the%20BJP's%20choice%20of%20Chief%20Ministers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20the%20signals%20they%20aim%20to%20send.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20replacing%20the%20incumbent%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20right%20after%20a%20resounding%20victory%20might%20have%20seemed%20like%20a%20formidable%20task.%20However%2C%20the%20new%20BJP's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20a%20generational%20change%20has%20emboldened%20it%20to%20make%20decisions%20that%2C%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20may%20appear%20risky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20new%20BJP%20has%20a%20systematic%20plan%20in%20place%20for%20effecting%20a%20generational%20shift%2C%20it%20boldly%20nominates%20candidates%20who%20might%20surprise%20traditional%20observers.%20These%20choices%20are%20made%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20party's%20future%20readiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20selection%20of%20Mohan%20Yadav%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20He%20represents%20the%20new%20generation%20of%20leaders%2C%20and%20is%20steeped%20in%20RSS%20culture%20since%20his%20student%20days.%20He%20is%20from%20a%20region%20in%20the%20state%20that%20has%20been%20a%20BJP%20stronghold%20and%20belongs%20to%20a%20social%20group%20that%20wields%20substantial%20influence%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20of%20generation-next%20in%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20selection%20is%20strategically%20aimed%20at%20making%20the%20BJP%20future-ready%2C%20not%20only%20within%20his%20state%20but%20also%20in%20neighbouring%20ones.%20By%20choosing%20him%2C%20the%20BJP%20not%20only%20consolidates%20support%20from%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%2C%20but%20also%20seeks%20to%20divide%20the%20Yadav%20community%2C%20which%20has%20largely%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20party%20in%20states%20where%20they%20hold%20sway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20selection%20of%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%2C%20a%20tribal%20leader%20who%20has%20risen%20through%20the%20ranks%2C%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20another%20attempt%20to%20attract%20a%20group%20that%20has%20been%20cautious%20in%20its%20support%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20have%20hinted%20at%20a%20willingness%20among%20tribal%20groups%20to%20change%20their%20political%20preferences.%20According%20to%20Election%20Commission%20data%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%20victory%20in%2017%20out%20of%20the%2029%20tribal-dominated%20seats%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20a%20significant%20increase%20from%20just%20three%20in%202018.%20Post-poll%20data%20of%20CSDS%20(Centre%20for%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies)%20also%20indicates%20that%20nearly%2046%20percent%20of%20tribal%20votes%20went%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20compared%20to%20just%2042%20percent%20for%20the%20Congress.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20dominated%20tribal-dominated%20seats%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20BJP%20chose%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20Brahmin%20leader%2C%20to%20lead%20the%20government.%20With%20a%20background%20in%20the%20RSS%20since%20his%20student%20days%2C%20he%20is%20a%20first-time%20MLA%20from%20the%20Sanganer%20assembly%20constituency%2C%20a%20seat%20the%20BJP%20has%20consistently%20won%20since%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20chief%20ministerial%20selections%20share%20a%20common%20theme%20-%20they%20have%20ascended%20through%20the%20ranks.%20This%20sends%20a%20resounding%20message%20to%20all%20party%20workers%20that%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BSabka%20time%20aayega%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20(everyone%20will%20get%20a%20shot%20at%20the%20top%20job).%20Political%20pundits%20emphasize%20that%20this%20message%20is%20crucial%20to%20keeping%20the%20BJP's%20well-oiled%20election%20machinery%20charged%20and%20motivated%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrast%20this%20with%20the%20generational%20landscape%20of%20top%20leaders%20within%20the%20Congress%2C%20across%20states.%20In%20the%20grand%20old%20party%2C%20proximity%20to%20the%20highest%20echelons%20of%20leadership%20has%20traditionally%20been%20the%20primary%20factor%20for%20advancement.%20This%20tendency%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20perception%2C%20both%20within%20the%20party%20and%20outside%20of%20it%2C%20that%20the%20Congress%20tends%20to%20operate%20in%20a%20rather%20insular%20manner%20at%20the%20highest%20levels.%20This%20perception%20has%20become%20a%20chronic%20issue%20that%20has%20adversely%20affected%20the%20party's%20electoral%20performance%20in%20election%20after%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Mayank%20Mishra%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702383960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F9nj6v24k_bhajan-lal-sharma-ani_625x300_12_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-bps-state-surprises-reveal-about-its-succession-planning-4660067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20the%20new%20BJP%20has%20a%20systematic%20plan%20in%20place%20for%20effecting%20a%20generational%20shift%2C%20it%20boldly%20nominates%20candidates%20who%20might%20surprise%20traditional%20observers.%20These%20choices%20are%20made%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20party's%20future%20readiness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-bps-state-surprises-reveal-about-its-succession-planning-4660067%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-bps-state-surprises-reveal-about-its-succession-planning-4660067%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-bps-state-surprises-reveal-about-its-succession-planning-4660067%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%3A%20First-Time%20MLA%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20Is%20New%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12175218%2FGBDRaWFW8AAmpdq.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20BJP%20has%20announced%20that%20first-time%20MLA%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20will%20be%20the%20next%20chief%20minister%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20while%20Diya%20Kumari%20and%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%20will%20be%20his%20deputies.%20The%20Ajmer%20North%20MLA%20Vasudev%20Devnani%20will%20be%20the%20assembly%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharma%2C%20the%2056-year-old%20MLA%20from%20Sanganer%2C%20is%20a%20long-time%20party%20member%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20ABVP%20during%20his%20student%20days.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-is-bjps-rajasthan-chief-minister-choice-4659836%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20general%20secretary%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20organisation%20man.%20Sharma%20has%20an%20MA%20in%20politics%20from%20Rajasthan%20University%20and%20has%20declared%20one%20criminal%20case%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20announcement%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20now%20dropped%20all%20of%20its%20previous%20chief%20ministers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan)%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20(Raman%20Singh)%20and%20Rajasthan%20(Vasundhara%20Raje).%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-yadav-little-known-outside-ujjan-bjps-cm-pick-for-mp-baffles-party-leaders-cadres%5C%22%3EMohan%20Yadav%20was%20chosen%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-bjp-ends-week-long-suspense-names-vishnu-deo-sai-as-next-chief-minister%5C%22%3EVishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20will%20lead%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%20asked%20Raje%20to%20propose%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20name%20as%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20at%20the%20legislature%20party%20meeting%20in%20Jaipur%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon.%20The%20central%20observers%20for%20the%20meet%20were%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Vinod%20Tawde%20and%20Saroj%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20five%20terms%2C%20either%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20or%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20have%20been%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20announce%20who%20its%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20was%20during%20the%20recently-concluded%20assembly%20elections%2C%20Raje%20and%20Union%20ministers%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%2C%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20and%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20were%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20frontrunners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20a%20convincing%20victory%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20bagging%20115%20of%20the%20199%20seats%20that%20went%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702383926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12175218%2FGBDRaWFW8AAmpdq.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-first-time-mla-bhajanlal-sharma-new-chief-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20this%20announcement%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20now%20dropped%20all%20of%20its%20previous%20chief%20ministers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan)%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20(Raman%20Singh)%20and%20Rajasthan%20(Vasundhara%20Raje).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-first-time-mla-bhajanlal-sharma-new-chief-minister%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindalco%20to%20invest%20Rs%20800%20cr%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20battery%20foil%20plant%20in%20Odisha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702383807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fhp%2Fhome-page%2F2023-08%2F08%2Ffull%2F1691493766-9643.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhindalco-to-invest-rs-800-cr-in-setting-up-a-battery-foil-plant-in-odisha-123121200886_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%