%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esue%20Cybertruck%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20they%20resold%20their%20vehicles%20within%20the%20first%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20buyer%20who%20ordered%20the%20limited%20launch%20edition%20%26quot%3BFoundation%20Series%26quot%3B%20Cybertruck%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farstechnica.com%2Ftech-policy%2F2023%2F12%2Ftesla-again-threatens-to-sue-cybertruck-buyers-who-try-to-resell-the-cars%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20told%20Ars%20Technica%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20contract%20they%20received%20from%20Tesla%20included%20the%20clause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20contract%2C%20which%20was%20reviewed%20by%20the%20technology%20website%2C%20required%20Cybertruck%20owners%20to%20offer%20the%20car%20back%20to%20Tesla%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20before%20attempting%20to%20resell%20it.%20It%20also%20said%20Cybertrucks%20could%20only%20be%20resold%20if%20Tesla%20provided%20owners%20with%20%26quot%3Bwritten%20consent%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20Ars%20Technica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20those%20terms%20were%20breached%2C%20the%20clause%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTesla%20may%20seek%20injunctive%20relief%20to%20prevent%20the%20transfer%20of%20title%20of%20the%20Vehicle%20or%20demand%20liquidated%20damages%20from%20you%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20%2450%2C000%20or%20the%20value%20received%20as%20consideration%20for%20the%20sale%20or%20transfer%2C%20whichever%20is%20greater.%20Tesla%20may%20also%20refuse%20to%20sell%20you%20any%20future%20vehicles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clause%20first%20appeared%20last%20month%20in%20an%20additional%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tesla.com%2Fconfigurator%2Fapi%2Fv3%2Fterms%3Flocale%3Den_US%26model%3Dmy%26saleType%3DSale%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esection%20of%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20EV%20company's%20Motor%20Vehicle%20Order%20Agreement%20titled%20%26quot%3BFor%20Cybertruck%20Only.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20section%20similarly%20said%20the%20company%20could%20sue%20f