e%20cites%20from%20the%20films%20some%20of%20them%20made%20during%20the%20strike%20where%20they%20themselves%20and%20others%20spoke%20about%20their%20fears%2C%20expectations%2C%20their%20determination%20not%20to%20yield%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98carrots%E2%80%99%20being%20held%20out%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20the%20core%20of%20the%20book%2C%20the%20primary%20motivation%20for%20writing%20it%2C%20it%20is%20by%20no%20means%20the%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20it.%20The%20whole%20thing%20is%20an%20intricate%20network%20of%20intersecting%20diachronic%20narratives%20and%20synchronic%20reportage%20encompassing%20the%20history%20of%20the%20FTII%20as%20an%20institution%20along%20with%20the%20nearby%20National%20Film%20Archive%20of%20India%20(NFAI)%2C%20the%20careers%20of%20FTII%20graduates%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20mainstream%20industry%2C%20the%20history%20of%20strikes%20at%20the%20FTII%2C%20the%20history%20of%20student%20strikes%20in%20general%20and%20especially%20the%20era%20of%20student%20actions%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20Jadavpur%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20the%20FTII%20strike%20was%20an%20early%20signal.%20Government%20policy%20measures%2C%20including%20committee%20reports%2C%20acts%20of%20parliament%2C%20censorship%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20an%20abiding%20concern%20of%20the%20author%20who%20has%20written%20extensively%20on%20these%20matters%20%E2%80%93%20prove%20salient%20to%20the%20many%20stories%20he%20interweaves%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12161554%2Fdownload-12.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22293%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688857%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22351%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAshish%20Rajadhyaksha%3Cbr%3EJohn-Ghatak-Tarkovsky%3A%20Citizens%2C%20Filmmakers%2C%20Hackers%3Cbr%3ESSAF-Tulika%20Books%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20is%20a%20telling%20history%20of%20cancelled%20screenings%20that%20is%20as%20central%20to%20these%20stories%20as%20it%20is%20to%20the%20republic%E2%80%99s%20rapidly%20declining%20political%20health%3A%20these%20too%20are%20detailed%20and%20some%20of%20them%20are%2C%20in%20retrospect%2C%20the%20immediate%20risk%20to%20lives%20having%20passed%2C%20quite%20amusing%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Kirori%20Mal%20college%20screening%20of%20%3Cem%3EMuzaffarnagar%20Baqi%20Hai.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20once%20the%20clich%C3%A9%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20inappropriate%3A%20this%20is%20the%20product%20of%20a%20labour%20of%20love.%20It%20is%20hard%20to%20think%20of%20anyone%20other%20than%20Rajadhyaksha%20undertaking%20such%20a%20unique%20project.%20The%20established%20distinctions%20between%20film%20studies%2C%20film%20history%2C%20film%20appreciation%2C%20film%20education%20are%20blurred%2C%20the%20industry%2C%20mainly%20Mumbai%2C%20features%20alongside%20the%20parallel%20cinema%2C%20the%20passage%20from%20celluloid%20to%20digital%20is%20captured%20in%20its%20own%20right%2C%20as%20much%20as%20for%20the%20vital%20role%20it%20began%20to%20play%20in%20the%20latter%20part%20of%20the%20strike%20period%2C%20marking%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20way%20the%20author%20handled%20the%20subject%20in%20his%20previous%20book%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Cinema%20in%20the%20Time%20of%20Celluloid%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20engaging%20and%20instructive%20profiles%20of%20the%20principal%20protagonists%20of%20the%20strike%2C%20Naveen%20Padmanabha%2C%20Ranjit%20Nair%2C%20Harishankar%20Nachimuthu%2C%20Vikas%20Urs%2C%20Kshama%20Padalkar%2C%20Kislay%2C%20Prateek%20Vats%20and%20as%20well%20as%20others%20who%20were%20not%20centrally%20involved%20in%20the%20strike%20%E2%80%93%20%C2%A0some%20of%20them%20even%20unhappy%20with%20the%20turn%20of%20events%20%E2%80%93%20the%20films%20they%20made%2C%20the%20problems%20they%20faced%20as%20a%20strike%20team%20and%20as%20individuals.%20Older%20graduates%20or%20near%20graduates%20make%20their%20appearance%20too%3A%20Paresh%20Kamdar%2C%20Farida%20Mehta%2C%20but%20also%20Ritwik%20Ghatak%2C%20Kundan%20Shah%2C%20Sudhir%20Mishra%2C%20Girish%20Kasaravalli.%20Indeed%2C%20all%20of%20Chapter%203%2C%20with%20the%20making%20of%20%3Cem%3EJaane%20Bhi%20Do%20Yaro%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20its%20centre%2C%20is%20a%20delightful%20read.%20Cameras%2C%20from%20the%20Mitchell%20to%20the%20latest%20digital%20offering%2C%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20strike%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20ecosystem%20has%20no%20place%20for%20close%20readings%20of%20films%2C%20Rajadhyaksha%20offers%20interesting%20takes%20on%20some%20of%20the%20graduates%E2%80%99%20films%2C%20notably%20Prateek%20Vats%E2%80%99%20%3Cem%3EEeb%20Allay%20Oo%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2019)%2C%20seeing%20in%20them%20a%20commentary%20on%20the%20state%20of%20things%20at%20the%20institution%20as%20well%20as%20the%20country%20as%20a%20whole.%20There%20is%20a%20staggering%20wealth%20of%20detail%20in%20this%20work%20that%20can%20scarcely%20be%20summarised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20difficulties%20of%20writing%20about%20an%20event%20like%20the%20FTII%20strike%20is%20that%20it%20is%20not%20sufficiently%20distant%20in%20time.%20Thus%20the%20story%20is%20presented%20as%20a%20chronicle%2C%20though%20not%20without%20extensive%20commentary.%20This%20time%20is%20still%20with%20us%2C%20the%20struggles%20that%20broke%20out%20then%20continue%20to%20flare%20up%20in%20institutions%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20English%20and%20Foreign%20Languages%20University%20(EFLU)%20as%20I%20write%20this%2C%20students%20demanding%20action%20against%20sexual%20harassment%20have%20faced%20a%20hostile%20administration%2C%20while%20one%20of%20them%20has%20been%20assaulted%20by%20hooded%20men%20in%20the%20style%20of%20the%20JNU%20infiltration%20of%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20But%20it%20is%20still%20worth%20noting%20the%20three%20to%20four%20years%20during%20which%20multiple%20strikes%20and%20movements%20erupted%20one%20after%20the%20other%2C%20connecting%20and%20supporting%20one%20another%3A%20Jadavpur%20University%20(Hokkolorob)%2C%20Jamia%2C%20Hyderabad%20Central%20University%20(Rohith%20Vemula)%2C%20JNU%20Freedom%20Square%2C%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%2C%20then%20the%20anti-CAA%20movement%20and%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20which%20besieged%20Delhi%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20returning%20of%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20200px)%2085vw%2C%20200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12161939%2F337528892_1155422449187054_7811838237578739008_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12161939%2F337528892_1155422449187054_7811838237578739008_n.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12161939%2F337528892_1155422449187054_7811838237578739008_n-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688858%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAshish%20Rajadhyaksha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20surprising%20is%20that%20one%20of%20the%20first%20of%20these%20was%20the%20FTII%20strike.%20From%20the%20history%20of%20student%20strikes%20in%20FTII%20traced%20in%20the%20book%20(chapter%202)%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20most%20of%20them%20were%20confined%20to%20matters%20of%20an%20intra-institutional%20nature.%20It%20is%20only%20in%202015%20that%20the%20strike%20acquired%20a%20wider%20significance%20of%20such%20magnitude%2C%20and%20became%20the%20harbinger%20of%20a%20season%20of%20struggles%20that%20have%20claimed%20many%20casualties%2C%20destroyed%20many%20futures%20but%20also%20stood%20as%20testament%20to%20the%20refusal%20to%20fall%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Rajadhyaksha%20the%20FTII%20strike%2C%20and%20indeed%20all%20the%20other%20struggles%20discussed%2C%20exemplify%20the%20%E2%80%98networked%20protest%E2%80%99.%20The%20key%20word%20here%20is%20%3Cem%3Ehorizontalism%3C%2Fem%3E.%20As%20he%20puts%20it%3A%20%E2%80%98As%20the%20agitations%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20processions%20and%20occupy%20movements%2C%20they%20also%20brought%20into%20India%20what%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%20worldwide%20as%20the%20networked%20protest%2C%20and%20by%20a%20term%20originally%20coined%20in%20Argentina%20in%20December%202001%20as%20%3Cem%3Ehorizontalidad%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20horizontalism.%20Seeking%20to%20overcome%20the%20traditional%20hierarchies%20of%20organized%2C%20leader-driven%20political%20action%2C%20the%20effort%20to%20create%20new%20democratic%20social%20spaces%20was%20enabled%20by%20new%20technologies%20permitting%20horizontal%20peer-to-peer%20circulation%2C%20authorless%20memes%2C%20and%20the%20rapid%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20or%20what%20the%202019%20Hong%20Kong%20protestors%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98being%20water%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20of%20data%2C%20ideas%20and%20human%20action.%E2%80%99%20(p6)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tahrir%20Square%20demonstration%2C%20the%20Occupy%20movement%2C%20both%20of%20which%20date%20to%202011%20perhaps%20helped%20to%20spread%20this%20terminology.%20That%20vision%20of%20ultimate%20human%20autonomy%20where%20no%20one%20needs%20lead%20another%20along%20the%20right%20path%20or%20any%20path%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20is%20of%20course%20familiar%20to%20us%20from%20the%20socialist%20literature.%20It%20is%20the%20final%20goal%20of%20prophetic%20texts%2C%20even%20scientific%20ones%20such%20as%20those%20of%20Marx.%20What%20is%20new%20in%20the%20invocations%20of%20horizontality%20is%20the%20suggestion%20that%20such%20a%20state%20might%20already%20have%20been%20achieved.%20And%20yet%20the%20struggles%20continue.%20What%20are%20we%20to%20make%20of%20this%20paradox%3F%20This%20is%20not%20the%20place%20to%20go%20into%20a%20discussion%20of%20such%20matters.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20in%20celebrating%20horizontality%20serious%20theoretical%20questions%20may%20have%20been%20ignored.%20Consider%20the%20slogans%2C%20which%20are%20given%20their%20due%20place%20in%20Rajadhyaksha%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20one%20that%20serves%20as%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20title%3A%20John%20Ghatak%20Tarkovsky%20%E2%80%93%20We%20shall%20fight%20we%20shall%20win%3B%20Go%20back%20Chauhan%2C%20Ghatak%20was%20here!%3B%20Eisenstein%2C%20Pudovkin%20%E2%80%93%20We%20shall%20fight%20we%20shall%20win.%20Were%20there%20no%20leaders%20of%20the%20FTII%20strike%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20I%20must%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20book%20as%20artifact.%20I%20have%20seen%20nothing%20that%20even%20remotely%20resembles%20it.%20Photographs%20in%20a%20book%2C%20of%20which%20there%20are%20plenty%20here%2C%20are%20nothing%20new.%20Nor%20is%20the%20inclusion%20of%20reproductions%20of%20archival%20documents%2C%20which%20fill%20many%20pages%20of%20this%20volume.%20(My%20favourite%20is%20a%20handwritten%20%E2%80%98chart%20of%20the%20genesis%20of%20FTII%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20pioneer%20of%20film%20appreciation%2C%20Satish%20Bahadur).%20What%20is%20new%20are%20the%20number%20of%20QR%20codes%20which%20take%20you%20to%20more%20documents%2C%20articles%2C%20reports%20and%20books%20easily%20amounting%20to%20a%20few%20thousand%20pages.%20Is%20it%20a%20book%3F%20Is%20it%20an%20archive%3F%20Is%20it%20an%20art%20installation%3F%20Hard%20to%20say%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20gripping%20documentation%20of%20an%20important%20moment%20in%20recent%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.%20Madhava%20Prasad%20is%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Cultural%20Studies%2C%20The%20English%20and%20Foreign%20Languages%20University%2C%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702382421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2Fftii-strikers.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-gripping-deep-dive-into-the-2015-ftii-students-agitation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashish%20Rajadhyaksha%E2%80%99s%20one-of-a-kind%20volume%20%E2%80%93%20John-Ghatak-Tarkovsky%3A%20Citizens%2C%20Filmmakers%2C%20Hackers%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20fairly%20comprehensive%2C%20non-linear%20chronicle%20of%20the%20strike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-gripping-deep-dive-into-the-2015-ftii-students-agitation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BStarc%20Would%20Take%20Away%20Millions...If%20He%20Backs%20Away%26quot%3B%3A%20Star%20On%20IPL%20Auction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20auction%20list%20is%20out.%C2%A0The%20list%20features%20333%20cricketers%2C%20who%20are%20scheduled%20to%20go%20under%20the%20gavel%20in%20Dubai%20on%20December%2019%2C%202023.%20Out%20of%20333%20players%2C%20214%20are%20Indians%20and%20119%20are%20overseas%20players%20of%20which%202%20players%20are%20from%20associate%20nations.%20The%20total%20capped%20players%20are%20116%2C%20uncapped%20players%20are%20215%20and%202%20from%20associate%20nations.%20A%20maximum%20of%2077%20slots%20are%20now%20available%20with%20up%20to%2030%20being%20slotted%20for%20overseas%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINR%202%20crore%20is%20the%20highest%20reserve%20price%20with%2023%20players%20choosing%20to%20be%20slotted%20in%20the%20highest%20bracket.%2013%20players%20are%20in%20the%20auction%20list%20with%20a%20base%20price%20of%20INR%201.5%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Australia's%20World%20Cup-winning%20stars%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Travis%20Head%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F62477-travis-michael-head-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETravis%20Head%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%