s%20made%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdaughter%20of%20Jaipur%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bprincess%20who%20walks%20on%20the%20streets%26quot%3B.%20The%20blend%20of%20regal%20heritage%20and%20a%20'relatable%2C%20down-to-earth%20persona'%20has%20made%20her%20a%20popular%20figure%20among%20the%20people%20of%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20joining%20the%20BJP%20in%202013%2C%20Diya%20Kumari%20has%20won%20the%20three%20elections%20she%20contested.%20She%20became%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20Sawai%20Madhopur%20constituency%20in%202013.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20she%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Rajsamand%20with%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20victory%20margins%20of%205.5%20lakh%20votes.%20She%20has%20now%20won%20the%202023%20Assembly%20polls%20from%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20campaign%20for%20the%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%2052-year-old%20made%20a%20pitch%20for%20the%20environment%2C%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20women's%20empowerment.%20In%202019%2C%20she%20was%20elected%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20government's%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrem%20Chand%20Bairwa%20is%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20Dudu%20Assembly%20seat%20near%20Jaipur.%20He%20won%20the%20November%2025%20election%20with%20a%20margin%20of%20over%2035%2C000%20votes%20against%20Babulal%20Nagar%20of%20the%20Congress.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20naming%20of%20Mr%20Bairwa%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20balance%20caste%20equations%20by%20naming%20a%20Brahmin%20face%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Rajput%20and%20scheduled%20caste%20leaders%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20ministers.%20The%20Bairwa%20community%20has%20traditionally%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20naming%20of%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%20may%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20strategic%20move%20by%20the%20party%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Surprises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20picked%20former%20cabinet%20minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%20for%20the%20top%20job%2C%20preferring%20him%20over%20the%20party's%20longest-serving%20chief%20minister%2C%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20go%20with%20tribal%20leader%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20over%20three-term%20chief%20minister%20Raman%20Singh.%20PM%20Modi%20had%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20tribal%20leader%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%2C%20and%20Mr%20Sai%20is%20also%20known%20to%20be%20favoured%20by%20the%20party's%20ideological%20mentor%2C%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702382400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F3sqfbhrg_diya-kumari-jaipur-royal-family-facebook-650_625x300_06_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprincess-who-walks-the-streets-diya-kumari-is-1-of-2-rajasthan-deputies-4660043%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20announced%20that%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20one%20of%20the%20frontrunners%20for%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post%2C%20and%20scheduled%20caste%20leader%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%20will%20be%20the%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprincess-who-walks-the-streets-diya-kumari-is-1-of-2-rajasthan-deputies-4660043%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprincess-who-walks-the-streets-diya-kumari-is-1-of-2-rajasthan-deputies-4660043%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprincess-who-walks-the-streets-diya-kumari-is-1-of-2-rajasthan-deputies-4660043%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohan%20Yadav%3A%20Little%20Known%20Outside%20Ujjain%2C%20BJP's%20CM%20Pick%20for%20MP%20Baffles%20Party%20Leaders%2C%20Cadres%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12170059%2FEffect-27.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhopal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Like%20everyone%20present%20in%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20newly%20elected%20163%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MLAs%20on%20December%2011%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%20was%20stunned%20when%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20election%20observer%20and%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20announced%20that%20three-time%20lawmaker%20from%20the%20Ujjain%20(South)%20seat%20is%20the%20party%20high%20command%E2%80%99s%20choice%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20was%20seated%20in%20the%20third%20row%20in%20the%20meeting%20when%20the%20announcement%20was%20made.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20utterly%20surprised%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20party%20has%20given%20such%20a%20big%20responsibility%20to%20a%20small%20worker%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20told%20the%20media%20after%20the%20meeting.%20It%20took%20a%20while%20for%20the%20import%20of%20the%20news%20to%20sink%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBafflement%20over%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20all-pervasive%20bafflement%20in%20the%20meeting%20was%20understandable.%20For%2C%20none%20of%20those%20present%20had%20the%20foggiest%20of%20idea%20that%20the%20party%20high%20command%20would%20prefer%20a%20district-level%20leader%20over%20an%20impressive%20array%20of%20claimants%20for%20the%20post%20who%20have%20spent%20decades%20carving%20out%20a%20niche%20for%20themselves%20in%20state%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20outgoing%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20had%20prior%20information%20about%20the%20sensational%20development.%20Khattar%20had%20told%20Chouhan%20to%20propose%20the%20name%20of%20Mohan%20Yadav%20in%20their%20meeting%20half%20an%20hour%20ahead%20of%20the%20MLAs%E2%80%99%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20high%20command%E2%80%99s%20diktat.%20With%20a%20heavy%20heart%2C%20Chouhan%20followed%20the%20order%20even%20as%20half%20a%20dozen%20claimants%20such%20as%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20and%20Prahlad%20Singh%20Patel%20gloomily%20looked%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloom%2C%20surprise%2C%20and%20suspense%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20while%20later%20Union%20agriculture%20minister%20Tomar%20got%20a%20consolation%20prize%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20post%20of%20assembly%20speaker.%20But%20the%20other%20probables%20remained%20unlucky.%20Their%20disappointment%20deepened%20when%20it%20transpired%20in%20the%20meeting%20that%20the%20high%20command%20had%20deprived%20them%20of%20the%20post%20of%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20as%20well.%20For%20the%20two%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20posts%2C%20the%20names%20of%20Jagdish%20Devra%20(a%20Dalit)%20and%20Rajendra%20Shukla%20(a%20Brahmin)%20were%20announced%20in%20the%20meeting%20itself.%20The%20episode%2C%20marked%20by%20gloom%2C%20surprise%2C%20and%20suspense%2C%20lasted%2045%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20news%20of%20Yadav%20having%20been%20picked%20up%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20big%20shoes%20of%20Chouhan%20spread%20everyone%20was%20stunned.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20are%20known%20for%20their%20penchant%20for%20springing%20surprises.%20But%20nobody%20had%20imagined%20that%20the%20element%20of%20surprise%20would%20stretch%20this%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FModi-Shah.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20president%20Amit%20Shah%20at%20the%20party's%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20meeting%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Delhi.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%2FBJP4Gujarat%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22924%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-199162%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22613%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20president%20Amit%20Shah%20at%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20meeting%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Delhi.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%2FBJP4Gujarat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20everywhere%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20in%20drawing%20rooms%2C%20in%20parks%2C%20on%20social%20and%20electronic%20media%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20spotted%20wrapping%20their%20heads%20around%20the%20big%20mystery%20as%20to%20what%20is%20so%20special%20in%20Yadav%20that%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20chose%20him%20for%20the%20hotly%20contested%20post%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-bjp-names-mohan-yadav-an-obc-leader-with-rss-roots-as-the-next-cm%5C%22%3EMP%3A%20BJP%20Names%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20an%20OBC%20Leader%20with%20RSS%20Roots%2C%20as%20the%20Next%20CM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20is%20common%20knowledge%20among%20MLAs%20that%20Yadav%20is%20considered%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20His%20sharp%20rhetoric%20about%20Hindutva%20is%20also%20not%20a%20secret.%20But%20in%20a%20party%20where%20pouring%20scorns%20against%20Muslims%20has%20become%20par%20for%20the%20course%2C%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20extreme%20views%20are%20not%20considered%20high%20enough%20qualification%20for%20the%20top%20job.%20Nor%20does%20his%20hailing%20from%20the%20Yadav%20community%20set%20him%20apart%20in%20a%20party%20in%20which%2047%20MLAs%20belong%20to%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20reality%20check%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20media%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20has%20been%20describing%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20selection%20as%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20master%20stroke.%20However%2C%20the%20reality%20check%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suggest%20so.%20The%20election%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mark%20a%20generational%20transition%20if%20this%20is%20what%20the%20BJP%20would%20like%20the%20world%20to%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2058%2C%20Yadav%20cannot%20be%20called%20young.%20Nor%20is%20he%20a%20face%20of%20generational%20change.%20His%20predecessor%20Chouhan%20is%20only%20six%20years%20older%20than%20Yadav.%20Chouhan%20was%2046%20years%20old%20when%20he%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20November%202005.%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20predecessor%20Uma%20Bharti%20was%20even%20younger%20(44)%20when%20she%20led%20the%20BJP%20to%20a%20spectacular%20victory%20in%202003.%20Also%2C%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20educational%20qualifications%20%E2%80%93%20Ph.D%2C%20MBA%2C%20LLB%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%93%20do%20not%20make%20him%20a%20unique%20scholar%20among%20the%20MLAs%20given%20his%20antecedents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYadav%E2%80%99s%20political%20trajectory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20parameter%20of%20organisational%20and%20parliamentary%20experience%20too%2C%20Yadav%20is%20no%20match%20to%20either%20Chouhan%20or%20Uma%20Bharti%2C%20his%20predecessors%20both%20of%20whom%20hailed%20from%20the%20OBC%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20assuming%20the%20office%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Chouhan%20had%20been%20elected%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20five%20times%20between%201991%20and%202005.%20In%20this%20period%2C%20he%20rose%20in%20the%20organisational%20ladder%20from%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Yuva%20Morcha%20(BJYM)%20to%20BJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20and%20state%20party%20chief.%20Uma%20Bharti%20had%20been%20a%20five-time%20MP%20and%20Union%20cabinet%20minister%20before%20she%20became%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Anyway%2C%20she%20was%20already%20a%20national%20leader%2C%20thanks%20to%20her%20role%20in%20the%20Ramjanambhoomi%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20responsibilities%20in%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20student%20and%20youth%20wings%20have%20been%20largely%20confined%20to%20the%20Ujjain%20district.%20His%20rise%20began%20with%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP).%20In%201982%2C%20he%20became%20the%20co-secretary%20of%20the%20student%20union%20of%20the%20Madhav%20Science%20College%20and%20became%20its%20president%20in%201984.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20he%20took%20charge%20as%20the%20city%20minister%20of%20the%20ABVP%20in%20Ujjain%20and%20became%20the%20department%20head%20in%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201988%2C%20he%20was%20the%20co-minister%20of%20the%20ABVP%E2%80%99s%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20unit%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20national%20executive.%20In%201989-90%2C%20he%20became%20the%20minister%20of%20the%20ABVP%2C%20and%20in%201991-92%2C%20its%20national%20minister.%20In%201993-95%2C%20he%20was%20the%20co-area%20in-charge%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%20Ujjain%20city%2C%20while%20in%201997%2C%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20Yuva%20Morcha%E2%80%99s%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20working%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201999%2C%20he%20was%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20BJP%20Yuva%20Morcha%E2%80%99s%20Ujjain%20division.%20Between%202000%20and%202003%2C%20he%20was%20the%20Ujjain%20district%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20in%202004%2C%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20working%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%202004%20and%202010%2C%20he%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Ujjain%20Development%20Authority%20(with%20the%20rank%20of%20state%20minister).%20During%202011-2013%2C%20he%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20State%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20Bhopal%20(with%20the%20rank%20of%20cabinet%20minister).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20working%20committee.%20During%202013-2016%2C%20he%20was%20the%20co-convener%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Sanskritik%20Prakoshth%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20became%20an%20MLA%20in%202013%20from%20the%20Ujjain%20South%20seat%20and%20was%20elected%20again%20from%20the%20same%20seat%20in%202018%20and%202023.%20Yadav%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20as%20cabinet%20minister%20for%20higher%20education%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20political%20trajectory%20only%20barely%20touched%20the%20state%20level.%20Outside%20Ujjain%2C%20and%20possibly%20Malwa%20region%2C%20Yadav%20was%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20a%20pan-MP%20leader%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20Uma%20Bharti%20and%20Chouhan%20who%20have%20pan-Madhya%20Pradesh%20following%2C%20especially%20among%20OBCs%2C%20Yadav%20was%20never%20known%20to%20have%20any%20significant%20sway%20over%20these%20intermediary%20castes%20beyond%20Ujjain.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20associated%20at%20the%20state%20level%20with%20any%20Yadav%20caste%20outfits%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20defies%20comprehension%20as%20to%20how%20his%20elevation%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20will%20favourably%20impact%20the%20OBC%20vote%20banks%20in%20the%20Yadav-dominated%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaste%20dynamics%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20different%20from%20the%20two%20big%20northern%20states.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20Yadavs%20account%20for%2012%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20subsumed%20OBC%20identities%20under%20its%20Hindutva%20umbrella.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%20is%20not%20the%20first%20chief%20minister%20in%20MP%20from%20the%20caste.%20Before%20him%2C%20Babulal%20Gaur%2C%20a%20Yadav%2C%20was%20in%20the%20post%20for%2015%20months%20in%202004-2005.%20He%20was%20unceremoniously%20ousted%20from%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20rich%20businessman%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20narrative%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20mounted%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20favoured%20media%20around%20Yadav%20is%20that%20the%20party%20has%20chosen%20a%20backward%20MLA%20from%20a%20humble%20background.%20Yadav%20was%20born%20in%20a%20small%20farmer%20family.%20His%20father%20ran%20a%20tea%20shop.%20But%2C%20today%2C%20he%20is%20a%20successful%20businessman%20with%20a%20considerable%20stake%20in%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20assets%20witnessed%20an%20exponential%20growth%20from%20Rs%2016%20crore%20(2013)%20to%2042%20crore%20in%2010%20years%20of%20his%20being%20an%20MLA%20and%20minister.%20In%20the%20affidavit%20he%20submitted%20for%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%2C%20Yadav%20declared%20his%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2031%20crore.%20The%20assets%20include%20land%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20love%20for%20acquiring%20land%20landed%20Yadav%20in%20a%20controversy%20in%20July%20this%20year.%20It%20was%20alleged%20that%20at%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20instance%2C%20the%20Ujjain%20administration%20changed%20the%20status%20of%2050%20out%20148%20hectares%20of%20land%20that%20was%20reserved%20for%20Simhastha%2C%20the%20regional%20congregation%20held%20every%2012%20years%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20from%20agricultural%20to%20residential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%2050-hectare%20land%20is%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Yadav%20and%20his%20kin.%20The%20Congress%20party%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move.%20It%20accused%20Yadav%20of%20trying%20to%20pressurise%20the%20administration%20to%20earn%20huge%20profits%20from%20the%20change%20in%20land%20use.%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Ujjain%20Paras%20Jain%20also%20joined%20the%20protest.%20In%20a%20core%20committee%20meeting%20in%20Ujjain%20over%20the%20master%20plan%2C%20Jain%20and%20Yadav%20had%20a%20strong%20altercation%20over%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20row%20snowballed%20in%20the%20media%2C%20outgoing%20CM%20Chouhan%20intervened%20and%20ordered%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20status%20of%20the%20disputed%20land%20as%20agricultural%20from%20residential.%20The%20urban%20development%20department%20soon%20followed%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20much%20to%20the%20annoyance%20of%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20not%20the%20only%20controversy%20Yadav%20got%20embroiled%20in.%20He%20was%20barred%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20from%20campaigning%20in%20the%20state%20by-polls%20for%20a%20day%20on%20October%2031%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20reprimanded%20him%20for%20using%20%E2%80%9Cintemperate%20language%20transgressing%20the%20limits%20of%20decency%E2%80%9D.%20Twenty-eight%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20gone%20for%20bypolls%20on%20November%203%2C%202020%2C%20following%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%20after%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20and%20his%20loyalist%20MLAs%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20an%20election%20meeting%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20Yadav%20threatened%20the%20Congress%20with%20dire%20consequences%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20good%20for%20good%20people%20and%20bad%20for%20bad%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20someone%20wrongs%20us%2C%20we%20will%20bury%20such%20people%20under%20the%20earth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20seen%20threatening%20in%20a%20viral%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20kicked%20up%20another%20controversy%20during%20the%20recent%20assembly%20election.%20A%20video%20went%20viral%20showing%20him%20using%20extremely%20foul%20language%20against%20party%20workers%20scuffling%20with%20him.%20The%20video%20was%20again%20in%20circulation%20on%20social%20media%20after%20he%20was%20elected%20leader%20of%20the%20BJP%20legislature%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunally%20sensitive%20Ujjain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUjjain%2C%20from%20where%20Yadav%20hails%2C%20is%20known%20as%20a%20highly%20communally%20sensitive%20district.%20Communal%20tension%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20often%20flares%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20blue-eyed%20boy%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20the%20CM-designate%20has%20thrived%20financially%20and%20politically%20by%20mouthing%20provocative%20language%20against%20Muslims.%20His%20strong%20pro-Hindutva%20stance%20brought%20him%20close%20to%20the%20Sangh.%20The%20RSS%20is%20said%20to%20have%20a%20major%20say%20in%20his%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702382180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12170059%2FEffect-27.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-yadav-little-known-outside-ujjan-bjps-cm-pick-for-mp-baffles-party-leaders-cadres%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20choice%20of%20the%2058-year-old%20OBC%20leader%20by%20the%20party%20leadership%20has%20defied%20all%20comprehension%20given%20that%20the%20other%20claimants%20for%20the%20coveted%20post%20have%20more%20experience%20and%20popularity.%20Is%20Yadav's%20elevation%20a%20master%20stroke%20as%20is%20being%20described%20by%20the%20media%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-yadav-little-known-outside-ujjan-bjps-cm-pick-for-mp-baffles-party-leaders-cadres%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flight%20to%20Detroit%20diverted%20to%20Canada%2C%20300%20passengers%20left%20stranded%20in%20barracks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702382050000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105935595%2Cimgsize-47762.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdelta-flight-from-amsterdam-to-detroit-diverted-to-canada-passengers-left-stranded-in-barracks%2Farticleshow%2F105935591.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22