C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105935412.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20sudden%20stepping%20down%20of%20Ravindar%20Bhakar%20has%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20the%20film%20industry%20that%20is%20now%20curious%20to%20know%20who%20takes%20his%20place.%20It%20is%20during%20his%20tenure%20that%20South%20actor%20Vishal%20had%20alleged%20corruption%20charges%20against%20the%20CBFC.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fcbfc-ceo-ravindra-bhakar-transferred-back-to-ministry-of-railways%2Farticleshow%2F105935412.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Real%20Story%20Behind%20Recent%20Electoral%20Choices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20assembly%20poll%20results%20have%20sparked%20considerable%20debate%20and%20controversy%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20the%20perceived%20North-South%20divide%20in%20India.%20This%20discussion%20has%20been%20fueled%20by%20the%20outcomes%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20November%202023%2C%20where%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20secured%20significant%20victories%20in%20the%20northern%20states%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20won%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Telangana%2C%20marking%20a%20stark%20political%20contrast%20between%20these%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20notable%20incident%20that%20has%20intensified%20this%20discussion%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bgaumutra%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20statement%20made%20by%20DMK%20MP%20DNV%20Senthilkumar%20S%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20comment%20was%20pejorative%20and%20has%20rightly%20sparked%20a%20controversy%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20backlash%20and%20discussions%20about%20the%20North-South%20divide%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narrative%20around%20these%20election%20results%20and%20the%20subsequent%20comments%20by%20political%20figures%20reflect%20an%20underlying%20assumption%20about%20the%20voting%20behavior%20in%20northern%20India.%20Critics%20argue%20that%20voters%20in%20these%20regions%20are%20not%20exercising%20their%20votes%20properly.%20Further%2C%20there%20is%20also%20an%20assumption%20that%20there%20exists%20a%20positive%20correlation%20between%20lower%20literacy%20levels%20and%20the%20electorate%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sentiment%20aligns%20with%20broader%20skepticism%20about%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20democratic%20systems.%20This%20skepticism%20questions%20whether%20elections%20produce%20governments%20that%20genuinely%20respond%20to%20the%20public's%20needs%2C%20a%20debate%20notably%20intensified%20by%20Christopher%20H.%20Achen%20and%20Larry%20M.%20Bartels%20in%20their%202016%20book%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BDemocracy%20for%20Realists%3A%20Why%20Elections%20Do%20Not%20Produce%20Responsive%20Government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20They%20critique%20the%20traditional%20view%20of%20democracy%2C%20which%20assumes%20voters%20are%20rational%2C%20well-informed%2C%20and%20capable%20of%20choosing%20the%20most%20competent%20party%20based%20on%20a%20careful%20assessment%20of%20policies.%20Thus%2C%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20propagating%20this%20north-south%20controversy%20might%20find%20solace%20in%20Achen%20%26amp%3B%20Bartels'%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20Western-based%20critique%20may%20not%20fully%20capture%20the%20complexities%20of%20voter%20behavior%20in%20developing%20nations%20like%20India.%20In%20states%20such%20as%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20recent%20electoral%20outcomes%20suggest%20that%20voters%20are%20capable%20of%20making%20informed%20decisions%20that%20influence%20policymaking.%20These%20regions%20have%20shown%20that%20electoral%20results%20often%20hinge%20on%20the%20government's%20performance%20and%20policy%20decisions%2C%20challenging%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20uninformed%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20indicates%20that%20good%20governance%20and%20fair%20policies%20can%20positively%20impact%20voter%20turnout.%20This%20relationship%20suggests%20that%20voters%20do%20respond%20to%20and%20reward%20sound%20policymaking%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20underestimation%20of%20voter%20decision-making%20abilities%20in%20Achen%20and%20Bartels'%20critique.%20The%20Indian%20electorate%20often%20views%20voting%20not%20just%20as%20a%20civic%20duty%20but%20as%20an%20endorsement%20of%20policies%20that%20tangibly%20impact%20their%20daily%20lives%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20findings%20of%20scholars%20like%20Bolsen%2C%20Ferraro%2C%20and%20Miranda%20(2014)%20and%20Nickerson%20and%20Arceneaux%20(2009).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20precisely%20what%20the%20results%20of%20these%20assembly%20elections%20were.%20They%20were%20an%20emphatic%20endorsement%20of%20policies%20that%20tangibly%20impacted%20the%20policies%20at%20the%20grassroots.%20People%20didn't%20vote%20just%20on%20the%20how%20the%20policies%20by%20the%20state%20government%20was%20promoting%20ease%20of%20living%20but%20also%20the%20efforts%20by%20the%20union%20government.%20In%20a%20decisive%20effort%20to%20ensure%20equitable%20access%20to%20fundamental%20necessities%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20as%20revealed%20in%20the%20Economic%20Survey%202020-21%2C%20provided%20bare%20necessities%20to%20every%20Indian.%20The%20Bare%20Necessities%20Index%20(BNI)%2C%20comprised%20of%20a%20holistic%20compilation%20of%2026%20indicators%2C%20is%20framed%20around%20five%20essential%20dimensions%3A%20water%2C%20sanitation%2C%20housing%2C%20micro-environment%2C%20and%20other%20vital%20services.%20The%20index%20serves%20as%20a%20pivotal%20tool%20to%20gauge%20the%20country's%20progress%20in%20fulfilling%20basic%20needs.%20The%20introduction%20of%20the%20BNI%20marked%20a%20significant%20milestone%2C%20reflecting%20the%20government's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20improving%20living%20standards%20for%20every%20Indian.%20Remarkably%2C%20the%20BNI%20demonstrated%20tangible%20progress%2C%20indicating%20that%20between%202012%20and%202018%2C%20access%20to%20basic%20needs%20had%20improved%20in%20every%20state%20across%20the%20nation.%20The%20access%20to%20basic%20necessities%20have%20further%20improved%20the%20constant%20efforts%20made%20by%20the%20Government%20through%20network%20of%20schemes%20like%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%2C%20National%20Rural%20Drinking%20Water%20Programme%2C%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20Saubhagya%20and%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20access%20to%20bare%20necessities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20improvement%20in%20access%20to%20bare%20necessities%20in%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20can%20be%20a%20significant%20factor%20in%20explaining%20the%20BJP's%20success%20in%20elections%20in%20these%20regions.%20When%20a%20political%20party%20focuses%20on%20development%20projects%20that%20directly%20impact%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20population%2C%20especially%20those%20at%20the%20lower%20economic%20stratum%2C%20it%20often%20gains%20political%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2Fbudget2021-22%2Feconomicsurvey%2Fdoc%2Fvol1chapter%2Fechap10_Vol1.pdf%5C%22%3Ethese%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20a%20visible%20transition%20from%20very%20low%20to%20medium%2C%20which%20essentially%20means%20that%20the%20levels%20of%20access%20to%20bare%20necessities%20between%202012%20and%202018%20increased%20significantly.%20These%20numbers%20would%20have%20further%20gone%20up%20owing%20to%20schemes%20like%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20Ujjwala%2C%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20etc.%20When%20the%20electorate%20experiences%20tangible%20benefits%20in%20their%20daily%20lives%2C%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20support%20the%20incumbent%20government%2C%20attributing%20their%20improved%20living%20standards%20to%20the%20policies%20and%20programs%20it%20has%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20proxy%20for%20gauging%20whether%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20at%20the%20grassroots%20have%20improved%20is%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20voting%20patterns%20of%20the%20women.%20Targeted%20development%20schemes%20have%20been%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20their%20strategy%2C%20with%20initiatives%20such%20as%20the%20'Ladli%20Behana'%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20financial%20aid%20scheme%20that%20contributed%20to%20significant%20improvements%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20in%20the%20lower%20economic%20strata.%20This%20focus%20on%20development%20has%20been%20a%20persuasive%20element%20in%20swaying%20voter%20sentiment%2C%20as%20tangible%20enhancements%20in%20living%20standards%20directly%20impact%20the%20electorate's%20daily%20lives%2C%20thereby%20garnering%20support%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20tandem%20with%20these%20development%20efforts%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20successfully%20rallied%20women's%20support%2C%20which%20has%20been%20crucial%20to%20their%20electoral%20strategy.%20Women's%20voter%20turnout%20has%20shown%20a%20remarkable%20upward%20trend%2C%20especially%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20it%20rose%20from%2070.1%25%20in%202013%20to%2076.0%25%20in%202023%20and%20remained%20high%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20The%20BJP's%20effective%20vote%20share%20among%20women%20has%20been%20notable%2C%20with%2050%25%20of%20women%20voters%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20expressing%20their%20support%20as%20per%20exit%20polls.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20employed%20a%20multifaceted%20outreach%20program%20that%20includes%20engaging%20first-time%20voters%2C%20organizing%20young%20women's%20conferences%2C%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20professional%20women%2C%20which%20likely%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20these%20states'%20electoral%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20assembly%20election%20results%20in%20India%20and%20the%20ensuing%20North-South%20controversy%20serve%20as%20a%20poignant%20reminder%20of%20the%20folly%20in%20underestimating%20the%20electorate.%20The%20mocking%20tones%20and%20sweeping%20generalisations%20that%20paint%20Northern%20states%20as%20less%20discerning%20or%20Southern%20states%20as%20inherently%20oppositional%20miss%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20matter%20-%20voters%20vote%20for%20development.%20The%20assembly%20elections%20of%202023%20have%20spoken%20volumes%2C%20not%20just%20through%20the%20ballot%20but%20in%20the%20tangible%20improvements%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%20due%20to%20effective%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assumption%20that%20voters%20in%20certain%20regions%20are%20less%20informed%20or%20incapable%20of%20making%20sound%20political%20decisions%20is%20not%20just%20condescending%20but%20patently%20incorrect.%20The%20results%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20underscore%20a%20truth%20often%20overlooked%3A%20people%20recognize%20and%20reward%20the%20efforts%20that%20directly%20impact%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20remember%20the%20real%20divide%20is%20between%20those%20who%20understand%20the%20aspirations%20of%20India's%20voters%20and%20those%20who%20choose%20to%20belittle%20them.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20the%20voter's%20wisdom%20prevails%2C%20guided%20not%20by%20unfounded%20biases%20but%20by%20a%20clear-eyed%20assessment%20of%20which%20policies%20and%20leaders%20will%20best%20serve%20their%20interests%20and%20uplift%20their%20lives.%20The%20results%20are%20a%20resounding%20statement%3A%20Indian%20voters%20are%20neither%20naive%20nor%20can%20they%20be%20taken%20for%20granted.%20They%20vote%20for%20progress%2C%20they%20vote%20for%20development%2C%20and%20they%20vote%20with%20the%20hope%20of%20a%20better%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBibek%20Debroy%20is%20the%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20%26amp%3B%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20Additional%20Private%20Secretary%20(Policy%20%26amp%3B%20Research)%2C%20EAC-PM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702381500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Flq9u46ag_bjp-generic-supporters-flag-pti_625x300_24_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-real-story-behind-recent-electoral-choices-4659120%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recent%20assembly%20poll%20results%20have%20sparked%20considerable%20debate%20and%20controversy%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20the%20perceived%20North-South%20divide%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-real-story-behind-recent-electoral-choices-4659120%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-real-story-behind-recent-electoral-choices-4659120%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-real-story-behind-recent-electoral-choices-4659120%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Warren%20Buffett's%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20has%20slashed%20its%20HP%20stake%20by%20nearly%2060%25%20in%203%20months%20-%20and%20looks%20to%20be%20cutting%20its%20losses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22879%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Warren%20Buffett%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6502d4d0992da60019ec1d3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWarren%20Buffett.%3Cp%3EAP%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBerkshire%20Hathaway%20sold%20another%2046%20million%20HP%20shares%20in%20October%20and%20November%2C%20filings%20show.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWarren%20Buffett's%20company%20has%20more%20than%20halved%20its%20stake%2C%20cutting%