%22%3A%22COP%3A%20Protecting%20the%20Lifestyle%20of%20the%20Well-Off%20For%20the%2028th%26nbsp%3BTime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12153224%2Fmike-marrah-x4QaRXytmow-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EReports%20are%20that%20in%202023%2C%20there%20have%20been%20times%20when%20the%20global%20temperature%20has%20been%20higher%20than%202%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20the%20pre-industrial%20level.%20This%20level%20of%20warming%20has%20been%20flagged%20as%20causing%20irreversible%20change.%20Already%20at%20the%20current%20average%20annual%20temperature%20level%20of%20about%201.3%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20pre-industrial%20levels%2C%20the%20number%20of%20extreme%20weather%20events%20has%20dramatically%20increased%2C%20resulting%20in%20growing%20distress%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOP28%20needed%20to%20plan%20for%20reversal%20of%20average%20global%20temperature%20from%20its%20current%20levels.%20But%20this%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20on%20the%20agenda.%20A%20mitigation%20fund%20with%20paltry%20contributions%20has%20been%20proposed.%20The%20steps%20being%20discussed%20and%20the%20urgency%20required%20to%20reverse%20the%20rising%20average%20temperatures%20are%20not%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20today%20is%20not%20just%20global%20warming%20but%20the%20multi-faceted%20environmental%20pollution.%20Oceans%20and%20fresh%20water%20bodies%20are%20being%20severely%20polluted.%20There%20is%20impact%20on%20marine%20life%20and%20contaminants%20(like%20micro-plastics%20and%20chemicals)%20are%20entering%20human%20food%20chains.%20Heavy%20chemicals%20and%20elements%20are%20damaging%20various%20human%20organs%20with%20consequences%20for%20human%20health%20and%20leading%20to%20the%20proliferation%20of%20diseases%20like%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProduction%2C%20consumption%20and%20pollution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergy%20is%20required%20for%20the%20production%20of%20goods%20and%20services%2C%20their%20distribution%20and%20finally%20for%20consumption.%20Different%20forms%20of%20energy%20are%20available%20like%20electricity%2C%20wind%20power%2C%20burning%20coal%2C%20gas%20and%20petroleum%20products.%20Some%20are%20more%20polluting%20than%20others.%20For%20instance%2C%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%20like%20coal%20and%20diesel%20pollutes%20more%20than%20wind%20power%20or%20electricity%20from%20solar%20panels.%20Solar%20panels%20directly%20convert%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20rays%20into%20electricity%20while%20wind%20and%20hydro-electricity%20come%20indirectly%20from%20solar%20energy.%20These%20sources%20directly%20produce%20little%20or%20no%20greenhouse%20gases.%20However%2C%20production%20and%20setting%20up%20of%20solar%20panels%20and%20wind%20turbines%20also%20results%20in%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFossil%20fuels%20are%20stored%20green%20matter%20over%20millions%20of%20years%20and%20their%20burning%20produces%20greenhouse%20gases.%20Since%20they%20are%20easily%20available%2C%20their%20consumption%20has%20risen%20dramatically%20over%20time%20and%20that%20is%20leading%20to%20a%20massive%20increase%20in%20greenhouse%20gases%20in%20air%20and%20global%20warming.%20So%2C%20one%20is%20talking%20of%20what%20is%20less%20polluting%20and%20which%20releases%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20greenhouse%20gases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20there%20are%20two%20problems.%20First%2C%20most%20of%20the%20energy%20is%20being%20derived%20from%20the%20wrong%20kind%20of%20sources%2C%20which%20pollute%20more%20than%20others%20and%20produce%20more%20greenhouse%20gases.%20Second%2C%20consumption%20is%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20so%20more%20energy%20is%20required.%20Consumption%20is%20of%20all%20kind%20of%20goods%20and%20services.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20produced%2C%20transported%2C%20distributed%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20which%20requires%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20as%20production%20becomes%20more%20concentrated%2C%20there%20may%20be%20economies%20of%20scale%20but%20more%20transportation%20and%20distribution%20are%20required.%20It%20is%20visible%20in%20the%20long%20supply%20chains%20and%20distribution%20networks.%20So%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20greater%20efficiency%20due%20to%20use%20of%20more%20energy%20efficient%20methods%20of%20production%20and%20transportation%2C%20overall%20energy%20consumption%20has%20continued%20to%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEssential%20and%20luxury%20consumption%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProduction%20and%20distribution%20is%20related%20to%20consumption%20by%20humans%20for%20improvement%20in%20their%20welfare.%20A%20part%20of%20the%20output%20is%20for%20investment%2C%20to%20enable%20production%20to%20both%20continue%20and%20increase.%20Another%20part%20of%20consumption%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20public%20goods%20which%20are%20jointly%20consumed%2C%20like%20army%2C%20parks%2C%20sewage%20and%20public%20health.%20So%2C%20to%20address%20the%20problem%20of%20pollution%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20address%20private%20consumption%2C%20government%20consumption%20and%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumption%20may%20also%20be%20characterised%20as%20essential%20and%20inessential.%20Food%2C%20water%2C%20clothing%20and%20housing%20are%20essential%20for%20life.%20Agriculture%20and%20livestock%20rearing%20which%20produce%20food%20are%20blamed%20for%20much%20of%20release%20of%20greenhouse%20gases.%20Apart%20from%20curbing%20waste%20in%20production%20of%20food%2C%20nothing%20much%20can%20be%20done%20about%20it.%20Public%20services%20are%20required%20for%20a%20civilised%20existence%20of%20citizens%2C%20so%20here%20too%20one%20can%20try%20to%20provide%20these%20more%20efficiently%20but%20these%20are%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20can%20be%20curbed%20is%20inessential%20and%20luxury%20consumption.%20This%20has%20become%20huge%20amongst%20the%20well-off%2C%20government%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20corporate%20sector%2C%20and%20can%20be%20curtailed%20to%20reduce%20pollution.%20Unfortunately%2C%20consumption%20has%20become%20the%20yardstick%20of%20standard%20of%20living.%20Vacations%2C%20eating%20out%2C%20travel%2C%20throwing%20away%20usable%20things%2C%20discarding%20rather%20than%20repairing%20gadgets%2C%20etc.%2C%20have%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20practice%20of%20the%20well-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20demonstration%20effect%20from%20rich%20countries%2C%20the%20well-off%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20have%20copied%20wasteful%20consumption.%20The%20poor%20and%20the%20middle%20classes%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20try%20to%20emulate%20these%20consumption%20patterns.%20Advertising%20is%20used%20by%20producers%20to%20induce%20more%20consumption%2C%20not%20only%20among%20the%20well-off%20but%20among%20the%20less%20well-off%20and%20the%20poor.%20They%20are%20euphemistically%20defined%20as%20aspirational%20or%20those%20who%20want%20to%20consume%20more%20and%20can%20be%20induced%20to%20consume%20more%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumerism%20has%20become%20ingrained%20in%20life.%20It%20stands%20for%20consumption%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20consumption.%20Tremendous%20amount%20of%20waste%20is%20generated%20in%20producing%20and%20throwing%20away%20things%20or%20in%20fancy%20packaging%2C%20luxury%20five%20star%20living%2C%20etc.%20The%20poor%20are%20not%20a%20part%20of%20such%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkewed%20consumption%20pattern%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20who%20is%20consuming%20how%20much%20and%20therefore%20responsible%20for%20how%20much%20of%20the%20pollution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20socio-economic%20survey%20of%202018%20can%20be%20used%20to%20get%20the%20approximate%20consumption%20pattern.%20Translated%20to%20the%20all-India%20level%2C%20it%20suggests%20that%2090%25%20of%20Indian%20families%20spent%20less%20than%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month.%20So%2C%20about%20120%20crore%20Indians%20consumed%20less%20than%20Rs%202%2C000%20per%20month.%20This%20gives%20an%20annual%20consumption%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%2028.8%20lakh%20crore.%2098%25%20of%20the%20families%20consumed%20less%20than%20Rs%2020%2C000%20per%20month.%20Assuming%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20month%20of%20family%20expenditure%20for%20those%20between%20the%2090%25%20and%2098%25%2C%20each%20individual%20in%20this%20bracket%20was%20consuming%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20month.%20Their%20consumption%20would%20be%20Rs%203.8%20lakh%20crore.%20This%2098%25%20has%20little%20spare%20resources%20to%20waste%20or%20spend%20on%20luxury%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%202%25%20of%20the%20families%20in%20India%20were%20rich%20and%20consumed%20the%20maximum.%20In%202018-19%2C%20national%20income%20was%20about%20Rs%20167%20lakh%20crore.%20Of%20this%20about%2058%25%20was%20private%20consumption%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2096.9%20lakh%20crore.%20Subtracting%20the%20consumption%20of%20the%2098%25%2C%20the%20consumption%20of%20the%20top%202%25%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20Rs%2064.3%20lakh%20crore%20or%20Rs%2023.8%20lakh%20per%20person.%20Their%20consumption%20was%2066.36%25%20of%20the%20total%20and%20they%20are%20the%20real%20polluters%20because%20they%20have%20the%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20luxury%20items%20and%20inessentials.%20The%20picture%20today%20will%20not%20be%20very%20different%20from%20that%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poor%20in%20India%20are%20also%20recyclers%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20waste%20produced%20by%20the%20well-off.%20So%2C%20their%20net%20environmental%20impact%20is%20smaller%20than%20implied%20by%20their%20consumption.%20The%20poor%20do%20cut%20corners%20and%20pollute%20but%20that%20is%20done%20for%20survival%20and%20not%20for%20luxury.%20Finally%2C%20the%20poor%20are%20also%20forced%20to%20produce%20cheaply%20for%20the%20developed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consumption%20of%20the%20well-off%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20imports%20of%20automobiles%2C%20electronic%20items%2C%20specialty%20items%2C%20etc.%20Even%20when%20these%20are%20produced%20in%20the%20country%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20parts%20are%20imported.%20To%20balance%20trade%2C%20exports%20are%20required.%20India%20exports%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20low%20and%20intermediate%20technology%20products%20like%2C%20textiles%2C%20leather%20goods%20and%20toys%20where%20it%20faces%20competition%20from%20the%20other%20developing%20world%20nations.%20So%20prices%20have%20to%20be%20kept%20low%20(competitive).%20This%20is%20achieved%20by%20sacrificing%20environmental%20standards%20and%20paying%20workers%20low%20salaries.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20developing%20world%20accepts%20a%20polluted%20environment%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20developed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECOP%20not%20discussing%20the%20real%20issue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028th%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20is%20taking%20place%20but%20the%20real%20step%20required%2C%20namely%2C%20cutting%20consumption%20globally%2C%20is%20not%20on%20the%20agenda.%20Use%20of%20cleaner%20energy%20sources%20will%20help%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20the%20free%20rider%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20each%20nation%20expects%20others%20to%20take%20the%20steps%20required.%20The%20rich%20nations%20are%20blaming%20India%20and%20China%20for%20being%20the%20big%20polluters%20now.%20The%20latter%20blame%20the%20rich%20nations%20for%20the%20historical%20accumulation%20of%20greenhouse%20gases%20and%20is%20asking%20them%20to%20pay%20for%20it%20and%20to%20make%20available%20new%20technologies%20to%20reduce%20production%20of%20greenhouse%20gases.%20The%20rich%20nations%20are%20not%20offering%20to%20lower%20their%20per%20capita%20consumption.%20They%20see%20this%20as%20a%20lowering%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20their%20people.%20The%20developing%20nations%20like%20India%20are%20not%20offering%20to%20pursue%20policies%20that%20would%20reduce%20the%20consumption%20of%20the%20well-off.%20They%20see%20this%20as%20a%20reduction%20of%20their%20growth%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20developing%20nations%20are%20protecting%20the%20interest%20of%20their%20corporations%20and%20their%20well-off%20whose%20growing%20consumption%20leads%20to%20higher%20profits.%20Both%20want%20to%20persist%20with%20growing%20consumption%20of%20their%20elite%2C%20corporate%20culture%20and%20wasteful%20governments.%20This%20shows%20where%20the%20real%20political%20power%20in%20the%20World%20lies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20slogan%201%25%20against%20the%2099%25%20is%20apt.%20The%20cost%20of%20deliberate%20obfuscation%20falls%20on%20the%20marginalised%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20the%20poorer%20nations%20or%20the%20poor%20in%20each%20of%20the%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20brief%2C%20climate%20change%20and%20growing%20pollution%20are%20upon%20us%20and%20imposing%20heavy%20costs%20on%20all.%20Yet%2C%20the%20political%20will%20to%20take%20the%20drastic%20steps%20required%20is%20missing.%20The%20time%20for%20taking%20incremental%20steps%20is%20over.%20The%20fear%20that%20cutting%20consumption%20and%20production%20will%20reduce%20welfare%20for%20the%20elite%20and%20reduce%20employment%20is%20unfounded%20because%20these%20can%20be%20achieved%20by%20cutting%20social%20waste%20and%20inessential%20consumption%20which%20will%20enhance%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20well-being%20by%20reducing%20pollution.%20A%20study%20from%20the%20SA%20showed%20that%20in%201980%2C%2050%25%20of%20the%20production%20was%20a%20waste.%20For%20India%2C%20in%202006%2C%2025%25%20was%20a%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20COP%20to%20make%20progress%2C%20the%20agenda%20of%20both%20the%20rich%20nations%20and%20the%20ruling%20classes%20of%20the%20developing%20countries%20has%20to%20be%20cutting%20wasteful%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArun%20Kumar%20is%20the%20author%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EUnderstanding%20Black%20Economy%20and%20Black%20Money%20in%20India%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702380623000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12153224%2Fmike-marrah-x4QaRXytmow-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop-protecting-the-lifestyle-of-the-well-off-for-the-28th-time%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20COP%20to%20make%20progress%2C%20the%20agenda%20of%20both%20the%20rich%20nations%20and%20the%20ruling%20classes%20of%20the%20developing%20countries%20has%20to%20be%20cutting%20wasteful%20consumption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop-protecting-the-lifestyle-of-the-well-off-for-the-28th-time%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20unveils%20Manish%20Malhotra-designed%20new%20uniforms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702380480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105934743%2Cimgsize-66038.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fair-india-unveils-manish-malhotra-designed-new-uniforms-for-cabin-cockpit-crew%2Farticleshow%2F105934297.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20India%20has%20revealed%20its%20new%20collection%20of%20uniforms%20designed%20by%20Manish%20Malhotra.%20The%20introduction%20of%20the%20new%20uniforms%20will%20be%20done%20in%20stages%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Air%20India's%20first%20Airbus%20A350.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fair-india-unveils-manish-malhotra-designed-new-uniforms-for-cabin-cockpit-crew%2Farticleshow%2F105934297.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22270%20Delta%20passengers%20were%20stranded%20at%20a%20remote%20Canadian%20military