%202019%2C%20and%20his%20son%20the%20national%20coordinator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20joins%20the%20ranks%20of%20family-controlled%20regional%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20RJD%2C%20DMK%2C%20YSRCP%2C%20TDP%2C%20BRS%2C%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20JMM%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20PDP%2C%20National%20Conference%2C%20NCP%2C%20and%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20parties%20have%20either%20completed%20a%20transition%20to%20newer%20generations%20like%20RJD%20(Tejashwi%20Yadav)%2C%20SP%20(Akhilesh%20Yadav)%2C%20DMK%20(MK%20Stalin)%2C%20YSRCP%20(Jagan%20Reddy)%2C%20Akali%20Dal%20(Sukhbir%20Badal)%2C%20JMM%20(Hemant%20Soren)%2C%20or%20are%20staring%20at%20a%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Most%20Regional%20Parties%20-%20Family%20Fiefdoms%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Most%20Regional%20Parties%20-%20Family%20Fiefdoms%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fl0eoq574_most-regional-parties-family-fiefdoms_625x300_12_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20Regional%20Parties%20-%20Family%20Fiefdoms%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20parties%2C%20the%20process%20was%20not%20smooth%20and%20the%20BSP%20is%20no%20exception%20as%20a%20section%20of%20disillusioned%20old%20guard%20look%20for%20greener%20pastures%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPower%20transfer%20is%20smooth%20when%20a%20party%20is%20in%20power.%20If%20a%20party%20is%20out%20of%20power%20it%20faces%20challenges%2C%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20did%20from%20the%20old%20guard%20in%20the%20Congress%20when%20he%20took%20over%20from%20his%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20party%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20is%20fighting%20an%20existential%20battle%2C%20having%20been%20reduced%20to%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Mayawati%20hopes%20young%20Akash%20can%20shore%20up%20the%20party's%20support%20base%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20not%20be%20easy%2C%20as%20Akash%20lacks%20the%20charisma%20of%20his%20aunt%20in%20her%20heydays.%20The%2028-year-old%20is%20more%20of%20a%20backroom%20boy%2C%20and%20may%20not%20be%20acceptable%20to%20the%20middle-aged%20or%20older%20voters%20of%20the%20BSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20face%20competition%20from%20leaders%20like%20Bhim%20Army's%20Chandrashekhar%20Azad%20%26quot%3BRavan%26quot%3B%20who%20is%20gaining%20traction%20among%20a%20section%20of%20Dalit%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20question%20is%20whether%20Dalit%20voters%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20accept%20Akash%20Anand%20as%20torchbearer%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebahujan%3C%2Fem%3E%20identity%20like%20they%20accepted%20his%20aunt%20Mayawati%20as%20Kanshi%20Ram's%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20already%20made%20significant%20inroads%20into%20the%20non-Jatav%20Scheduled%20Caste%20vote%20in%20UP%2C%20bagging%2051%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20community's%20support.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20BSP%20has%20dropped%20to%20the%20third%20place%20among%20non-Jatavs%2C%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20emerging%20as%20their%20second%20choice%20in%20the%202022%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20is%20largely%20left%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Jatavs%2C%20the%20community%20that%20Mayawati%20belongs%20to%3B%2062%25%20of%20them%20supported%20the%20BSP%20in%202022.%20Whether%20London-educated%20city%20slicker%20Akash%20can%20establish%20a%20rapport%20with%20the%20BSP's%20traditional%20voters%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20aggressively%20wooing%20the%20Jatavs%20through%20representation%20in%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath-led%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20cabinet.%20It%20recently%20made%20Jagdish%20Devda%2C%20a%20Dalit%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%20was%20focussing%20on%20the%20five%20states%20that%20voted%20recently%20and%20where%20the%20BSP's%20performance%20remained%20poor.%20The%20party%2C%20which%20won%20six%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%20in%202018%2C%20was%20reduced%20to%20two%20seats.%20It%20couldn't%20open%20its%20account%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20it%20had%20won%20two%20seats%20each%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20my%20research%2C%20regional%20parties%20have%20an%20average%20life%20of%20around%2040%20years.%20Many%20regional%20parties%20are%20no%20longer%20in%20existence%2C%20having%20been%20subsumed%20by%20national%20parties%20or%20having%20acquired%20a%20new%20identity.%20There%20is%20a%20significant%20churn%20among%20these%20parties%20at%20the%20national%20and%20state%20level%3B%20Akash%20needs%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20BSP%20will%20be%20reaching%20that%20point%20soon%20next%20year%2C%20founded%20as%20it%20was%20in%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20won%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20and%20will%20struggle%20to%20retain%20these%20in%202024%20without%20joining%20either%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20or%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA.%20So%20far%2C%20it%20has%20maintained%20an%20equidistant%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20doesn't%20require%20the%20BSP's%20official%20support%2C%20while%20a%20Samajwadi-BSP-Congress%20alliance%20in%20UP%20looks%20difficult.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20the%20strain%20in%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20an%20alliance%20between%20Mayawati%2C%20Congress%20and%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati's%20party%20is%20going%20through%20a%20rough%20patch%2C%20and%20whether%20Akash%20can%20help%20the%20party%20%26quot%3Bsurvive%20and%20revive%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20new%20era%20is%20an%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20managed%20to%20add%20a%20seasoning%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20class%20to%20the%20Hindi%20heartland's%20caste%20based%20politics.%20It%20has%20tried%20to%20pull%20in%20many%20SC%20voters%20in%20its%20overarching%20Hindutva%20umbrella%2C%20w