.%20Immediately%2C%20executives%20started%20inquiring%20about%20what%20went%20wrong%20and%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20Sam%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Microsoft's%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Kevin%20Scott%20was%20informed%20by%20OpenAI's%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Mira%20Murati%20about%20the%20same.%20She%20added%20that%20she%20would%20be%20named%20as%20the%20interim%20CEO.%20%C2%A0At%20Microsoft's%2C%20Washington%2C%20headquarters%2C%20Mr%20Scott%20asked%20someone%20to%20inform%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20immediately%20even%20though%20he%20was%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20senior%20executives.%20The%20report%20states%20that%20Mr%20Nadella%20was%20shocked%20and%20called%20Ms%20Murati%20about%20the%20OpenAI%20board's%20reasoning.%20The%20board%20had%20said%20that%20Mr%20Altman%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20consistently%20candid%20in%20his%20communications%26quot%3B%20and%20Ms%20Murati%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20have%20answers%26quot%3B%20to%20such%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20is%20still%20unclear%20what%20led%20to%20Mr%20Altman's%20ouster%2C%20the%20CEO%20has%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fblessing-in-disguise-sam-altman-reflects-on-being-fired-as-openai-ceo-4651540%5C%22%3Ethat%20he%20still%20has%20some%20hard%20feelings%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20whole%20ordeal.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20very%20painful%20thing%20and%20felt%20to%20me%2C%20personally%2C%20just%20as%20a%20human%2C%20super%20unfair%20-%20the%20way%20it%20was%20handled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20Trevor%20Noah%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Now%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Altman%20was%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20for%20the%20Formula%20One%20Grand%20Prix%20when%20he%20got%20the%20news%20that%20the%20board%20had%20sacked%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20got%20to%20watch%20any%20race%20that%20whole%20weekend.%20I%20was%20in%20my%20hotel%20room%2C%20took%20this%20call%2C%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20was%20gonna%20be%2C%20and%20got%20fired%20by%20the%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Altman%2C%20his%20phone%20began%20to%20overflow%20with%20texts%20to%20the%20point%20that%20iMessage%20stopped%20functioning.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20in%20the%20next%20like%20half%20hour%2C%20I%20got%20so%20many%20messages%20that%20iMessage%20like%20broke%20on%20my%20phone.%20My%20phone%20was%20just%20unusable%20because%20it%20was%20just%20like%20notifications%20non-stop%20and%20iMessage%20like%20hit%20this%20thing%20where%20it%20stopped%20working%20for%20a%20while.%20That%20message%20got%20delivered%20late%2C%20then%20it%20marked%20everything%20as%20read%2C%20so%20I%20couldn't%20even%20like%20tell%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Altman%20looked%20and%20the%20bright%20side%20and%20stated%20that%20he%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20the%20whole%20incident%20despite%20its%20%26quot%3Bpainful%20cost%26quot%3B.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20empathy%20I%20gained%20out%20of%20this%20whole%20experience%2C%20and%20my%20recompilation%20of%20values%2C%20for%20sure%20was%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise.%20It%20was%20at%20a%20painful%20cost%2C%20but%20I'm%20happy%20to%20have%20had%20the%20experience%20in%20that%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702379700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fimd060g_sam-altman-reuters_625x300_08_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecret-whatsapp-group-with-over-100-ceos-as-member-comes-to-light-after-sam-altman-crisis-report-4659988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSam%20is%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20text%20said.%20Immediately%2C%20executives%20started%20inquiring%20about%20what%20went%20wrong%20and%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20Sam%20do%3F%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsecret-whatsapp-gr