0revealed%20that%20she%20was%20shot%2012%20times%20by%20Hamas%20operatives%20during%20their%20October%207%20attack%2C%20giving%20details%20about%20her%20survival.%20In%20an%20emotional%20post%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.october7.org%2Fpost%2Fi-waited-for-the-final-bullet-that-would-hit-me-and-kill-me%5C%22%3EOctober7.org%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20website%20with%20a%20list%20of%20survivor%20stories%2C%20First%20Lieutenant%20Eden%20Ram%20said%20she%20lay%20motionless%20among%20her%20dead%20friends%20%26quot%3Bwaiting%20for%20the%20final%20bullet%26quot%3B.%20Israel%20said%201%2C200%20people%20were%20killed%20when%20Hamas%20fighters%20raided%20border%20towns%2C%20kibbutzim%20and%20a%20music%20festival%2C%20and%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20taken%20to%20Hamas-ruled%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soldier%20started%20the%20post%20with%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20this%20is%20my%20story%2C%20the%20horror%20movie%20I%20lived%20through%20on%20Saturday%2C%20October%207%2C%202023.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20First%20Lieutenant%20then%20said%20she%20was%20trapped%20in%20a%20room%20along%20with%20six%20of%20her%20colleagues%20after%20being%20shot%20in%20the%20leg.%20The%20seven%20soldiers%20couldn't%20do%20anything%20but%20wait%20until%20Hamas%20blew%20through%20every%20security%20door%20until%20they%20finally%20reached%20the%20IDF%20troops%2C%20unleashing%20a%20volley%20of%20gunfire%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20this%20I%20was%20not%20sure%20if%20I%20was%20dead%20or%20alive%2C%20I%20felt%20dead%2C%20but%20I%20could%20still%20see%20and%20hear%20and%20feel.%20I%20waited%20for%20the%20final%20bullet%20that%20would%20hit%20me%20and%20kill%20me%2C%20but%20it%20never%20came%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20First%20Lieutenant%20Eden%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soldier%20further%20said%20that%20she%20was%20lying%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20own%20blood%20between%20the%20bodies%20of%20her%20friends%20for%20four%20hours%20as%20terrorists%20checked%20on%20the