ty-says-it-hurts-him-100-times-more-than-kl-rahul-and-athiya-shetty-when-people-troll-the-cricketer-reveals-he-sat-on-the-floor-to-watch-the-entire-world-cup%2Farticleshow%2F105932948.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%2C%20Expected%20To%20Be%20Republic%20Day%20Chief%20Guest%2C%20May%20Not%20Visit%20India%20In%20Jan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20travel%20to%20India%20next%20month%20to%20grace%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20as%20the%20Chief%20Guest%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Biden%20understood%20to%20have%20not%20planned%20a%20trip%20to%20India%20in%20January%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20summit%20of%20four-nation%20coalition%20Quad%20is%20also%20not%20taking%20place%20next%20month%20as%20expected%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20invited%20President%20Biden%20to%20be%20the%20Chief%20Guest%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20on%20January%2026.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20no%20comment%20by%20India%20on%20the%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20sources%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20the%20Quad%20summit%20is%20not%20taking%20place%20in%20India%20in%20January%20and%20it%20is%20now%20proposed%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20later%20part%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20expected%20that%20the%20Quad%20summit%20would%20take%20place%20around%20January%2027%20if%20Biden%20accepted%20India's%20invite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Quad%20Summit%20in%20India%20is%20proposed%20to%20be%20held%20later%20in%202024.%20We%20are%20looking%20for%20revised%20dates%20as%20the%20dates%20currently%20under%20consideration%20do%20not%20work%20with%20all%20the%20Quad%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%20or%20Quadrilateral%20coalition%20comprises%20India%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Japan%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20Washington%20has%20indicated%20to%20New%20Delhi%20that%20President%20Biden%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20travel%20to%20India%20for%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20flurry%20of%20visits%20by%20senior%20US%20officials%20to%20India%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20and%20Defence%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20visited%20India%20for%20the%20'2%2B2'%20ministerial%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Principal%20Deputy%20NSA%20Jonathan%20Finer%20visited%20India%20last%20week%20and%2C%20currently%2C%20FBI%20Director%20Christopher%20Wray%20is%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20by%20Finer%20and%20Wray%20came%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Washington's%20allegations%20about%20an%20Indian%20link%20to%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20on%20American%20soil.%20American%20prosecutors%20linked%20an%20Indian%20official%20to%20a%20man%20charged%20with%20conspiring%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%20India%20has%20already%20constituted%20a%20probe%20team%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Quad%20summit%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20that%20India%20is%20looking%20at%20fresh%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Quad%20summit%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20Hiroshima%20on%20May%2020%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G7%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%20summit%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Sydney%20on%20May%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20hold%20it%20in%20Hiroshima%20after%20President%20Biden%20postponed%20his%20trip%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3