%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688837%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBenjamin%20Zephaniah.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BZephaniah%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20a%20radiant%20presence%20and%20a%20gentleman.%20Zephaniah%20was%20not%20in%20the%20least%20condescending%20to%20someone%20like%20me%20who%20was%20yet%20to%20publish%20anything%20besides%20occasional%20poetry%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20very%20refreshing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workshop%20Chatterji%20was%20conducting%2C%20along%20with%20bookmaker%20Priya%20Pereira%2C%20focussed%20on%20the%20joys%20of%20writing%20a%20nonsense%20rhyme%20and%20creating%20a%20book.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20adults%20were%20very%20cynical%20about%20nonsense%20poetry%2C%E2%80%9D%20remembers%20Chatterji%2C%20who%20would%20in%202004%20publish%20an%20English%20translation%20of%20Bengali%20poet%20Sukumar%20Ray%E2%80%99s%20legendary%20book%20of%20nonsense%20rhymes%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAbol%20Tabol%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20explain%20in%20great%20detail%20how%20nonsense%20poetry%20makes%20children%20use%20parts%20of%20their%20brain%20to%20understand%20language.%20Zephaniah%2C%20however%2C%20knew%20immediately%20what%20I%20was%20talking%20about.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20vitality%20is%20what%20I%20remember%20from%20so%20many%20years%20ago%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZephaniah%E2%80%99s%20vitality%20also%20made%20quite%20an%20impression%20on%20me%20when%20I%20heard%20him%20at%20my%20alma%20mater%2C%20Jadavpur%20University%20in%20Kolkata.%20This%20was%20during%20another%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20India.%20Trying%20to%20confirm%20my%20memories%2C%20I%20called%20my%20professor%20Abhijit%20Gupta%20who%20is%20a%20senior%20faculty%20member%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20English%20of%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20March%202007%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20told%20me.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20after%20the%20Nandigram%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2014%20that%20year%2C%20the%20police%20opened%20fire%20on%20farmers%20protesting%20against%20attempts%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20then%20under%20the%20Left%20Front%2C%20to%20acquire%20land%20and%20create%20a%20special%20economic%20zone%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Nandigram%2C%20about%20130%20km%20southwest%20of%20Kolkata.%20Fourteen%20farmers%20were%20killed%20and%20100%20were%20reported%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20and%20some%20faculty%20members%20at%20Jadavpur%20University%20were%20protesting%20against%20the%20violence.%20The%20state-wide%20protests%20around%20Nandigram%20and%20Singur%2C%20another%20village%20where%20the%20government%20was%20trying%20to%20acquire%20land%2C%20would%20snowball%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20would%2C%20in%202011%2C%20lead%20to%20the%20leftist%20state%20government%20being%20voted%20out%20after%2034%20years%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20introducing%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gupta.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20I%20told%20the%20audience%3A%20%E2%80%98Keep%20your%20questions%20short.%E2%80%99%20Zephaniah%2C%20who%20was%20more%20than%206%20feet%20tall%20and%20towered%20over%20me%2C%20replied%20without%20missing%20a%20beat%3A%20%E2%80%98I%20like%20my%20questions%20big%20and%20muscular.%E2%80%99%20The%20audience%20erupted%20into%20peals%20of%20laughter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20listening%20to%20him%20perform%20his%20poem%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da3HjMcY50Kc%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%253Da3HjMcY50Kc%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702438151803000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1lYRIuEwd3DquR9pZK91sL%5C%22%3ERong%20Radio%20Station%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20visceral%20critique%20of%20state-sponsored%20propaganda.%20Now%2C%2015%20years%20later%2C%20as%20the%20media