-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-dismisses-plea-claiming-overvaluation-in-imported-goods-by-adani-123032800508_1.html%5C%22%3Eheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20all%20the%20imports%20were%20genuine.%20It%20concluded%20that%20the%20value%20declared%20was%20correct%20and%20was%20not%20required%20to%20be%20re-determined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20filings%20indicate%20that%20in%20April%202016%2C%20PMC%E2%80%99s%20engineering%20business%20was%20integrated%20into%20Howe.%20Recent%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20analyses%20of%20filings%20reveal%20that%20Howe%20continues%20to%20serve%20as%20an%20Adani%20contractor%20for%20some%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20ports%20and%20railway%20lines%20currently%20under%20construction%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Deloitte%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20determine%20whether%20Howe%20should%20be%20labelled%20a%20related%20party%20was%20why%20the%20auditor%20raised%20red%20flags%20about%20payments%20by%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20ports%20company%20to%20the%20contracting%20firm%20in%20May%2C%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accounting%20giant%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-resigns-as-the-statutory-auditors-of-adani-ports-and-special-economic-zone%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20auditor%20for%20Adani%20Ports%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20Ltd.%20in%20August%2C%20saying%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20sufficiently%20wide%20oversight%20over%20the%20broader%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Hindenburg%20Research%20directly%20called%20out%20PMC%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20alleging%20it%20was%20an%20Adani%20related%20party%20%E2%80%9Cused%20to%20suck%20money%20out%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20publicly%20listed%20entities.%E2%80%9D%20Its%20report%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20Howe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindenburg%20report%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CPMC%20Projects%20%E2%80%93%20a%20major%20contractor%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20%E2%80%93%20generated%20Rs%2063%20Billion%20(%24784%20Million)%20in%20revenue%20in%20the%20past%2012%20years.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20entity%20lacks%20a%20website.%20Records%20indicate%20its%20association%20with%20Adani%2C%20sharing%20the%20corporate%20address%20and%20phone%20number%20with%20the%20conglomerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20short-seller%20had%20also%20sought%20clarification%20on%20whether%20PMC%20Projects%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdummy%20firm%E2%80%9D%20affiliated%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Adani%20conglomerate%20told%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Howe%20and%20PMC%20are%20independently%20operated%20and%20managed%20companies%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20Adani%20related%20parties%20and%20all%20transactions%20are%20compliant%20with%20the%20law.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20commercial%20and%20business%20transactions%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Adani%20entities%20for%20project%20management%20services%20were%20entered%20into%20in%20the%20ordinary%20course%20of%20business%20at%20arm%E2%80%99s%20length%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%E2%80%99s%20son%20owns%20PMC%20Projects%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US-based%20short%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%2C%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%20has%20been%20alleged%20to%20have%20made%20considerable%20profits%20by%20buying%20and%20selling%20Adani%20stock%20through%20offshore%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20companies%20designate%20contractors%20as%20related%20parties%20in%20their%20accounting%20procedures%2C%20payments%20go%20through%20scrutiny%20from%20auditors%20and%20the%20board.%20However%2C%20as%20Adani%20maintains%20that%20Howe%20and%20PMC%20are%20not%20related%20parties%2C%20the%20group%20is%20exempt%20from%20subjecting%20Howe%20payments%20to%20additional%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%20the%20office%20of%20Hi%20Lingos%20Co%20Ltd.%2C%20where%20Chung-ling%2C%20the%20father%2C%20is%20the%20registered%20owner%20in%20Taiwan.%20The%20office%20prominently%20displayed%20the%20Adani%20logo.%20An%20office%20secretary%20said%20that%20Chung-ling%20declined%20an%20interview.%20When%3Cem%3E%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20a%20provided%20number%20for%20the%20son%2C%20the%20person%20who%20answered%20initially%20questioned%20the%20source%20of%20the%20number%20but%20later%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20not%20Chang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20had%20never%20publicly%20disclosed%20the%20payments%20to%20Howe%20until%20Deloitte%20flagged%20them%20in%20May%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20%24245%20million%20of%20refundable%20deposits%20was%20returned%20by%20Howe%20to%20Adani%20since%20then.%20Contractors%20typically%20return%20these%20funds%20once%20a%20project%20is%20completed%20or%20terminated%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20is%20who%20is%20getting%20the%20money%2C%20what%20work%20are%20they%20doing%20for%20Howe%20and%20Adani%2C%20how%20is%20the%20money%20being%20spent%3F%E2%80%9D%20Sharmila%20Gopinath%2C%20a%20specialist%20advisor%20for%20India%20at%20the%20Hong%20Kong-based%20Asian%20Corporate%20Governance%20Association%2C%20asked%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20reason%20is%20there%20not%20to%20disclose%20these%20payments%20when%20there%20are%20obviously%20deep%20ties%20with%20these%20people%2C%20with%20the%20owner%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20says%20that%20Howe%20is%20not%20a%20connected%20entity%2C%20but%20governance%20expert%20Gopinath%20contends%20that%20the%20significant%20payments%20made%20by%20Adani%20to%20the%20contractor%2C%20whose%20ultimate%20owners%20are%20Taiwanese%20associates%2C%20should%20have%20been%20declared%20as%20related%20party%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20rules%20on%20the%20matter%20can%20be%20open%20to%20interpretation%3B%20disclosure%20is%20required%20for%20transactions%20where%20one%20party%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20control%20or%20significantly%20influence%20the%20other%E2%80%99s%20financial%20and%20operational%20decisions%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccounting%20experts%20suggest%20that%20shared%20resources%2C%20employees%2C%20or%20directors%20overseeing%20common%20projects%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20related%20parties%2C%20subjecting%20payments%20to%20additional%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20board%20and%20auditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20cited%20the%20filings%20to%20highlight%20a%20revolving%20door%20of%20employees%20between%20Adani%2C%20Howe%2C%20and%20PMC%2C%20with%20past%20directors%20from%20Howe%20and%20PMC%20also%20appointed%20to%20Adani%20group%20company%20boards%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopinath%20told%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20more%20scrutiny%20is%20needed%20across%20India%20to%20assess%20payments%20by%20listed%20companies%20because%20investor%20money%20is%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702377034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17154946%2Fimage-1516.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-groups-ties-with-controversial-contractor-howe-raise-governance-concerns-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bloomberg%20reported%20that%20the%20contracting%20firm%20contains%20the%20core%20operations%20of%20a%20business%20called%20PMC%20Projects%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20PMC%20Projects%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20firms%2C%20faced%20allegations%20of%20inflating%20the%20value%20of%20imported%20power%20and%20infrastructure%20goods%2C%20amounting%20to%20nearly