from%20Campus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F06144304%2Fdu-protest.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20known%20for%20its%20robust%20student%20movements%2C%20will%20now%20penalise%20protests%20on%20campus%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20according%20to%20new%20rules%20released%20by%20the%20university%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rules%20of%20Discipline%20and%20Proper%20Conduct%20of%20Students%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20by%20the%20Chief%20Proctor%E2%80%99s%20Office%20were%20approved%20by%20the%20University%E2%80%99s%20Executive%20Council%20on%20November%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manual%20states%20that%20based%20on%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20actions%20either%20one%20or%20two%20punishments%20will%20be%20handed%20out%2C%20which%20include%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%3B%20up%20to%20two%20semester%E2%80%99s%20eviction%20from%20the%20hostel%2C%20rustication%2C%20and%20declaring%20out%20of%20bounds%20from%20entire%20JNU%20campus%20for%20up%20to%20two%20semesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEither%20one%20or%20two%20of%20these%20punishments%20will%20be%20handed%20out%20for%20%E2%80%9Chunger%20strikes%2C%20dharnas%2C%20group%20bargaining%20and%20any%20other%20form%20of%20protest%20within%20a%20100-metre%20radius%20of%20any%20academic%20and%20administrative%20complexes%20and%2For%20by%20blocking%20entrance%20or%20exit%20of%20any%20academic%20and%20administrative%20complexes%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdisrupting%20the%20movement%20of%20any%20member%20of%20the%20University%20community%20in%20administration%2C%20academic%20complexes%2C%20etc%E2%80%9D%2C%20violation%20of%20rules%2Forders%2Fcirculars%20of%20competent%20authority%2C%20Obstruction%2Fdamage%20of%20electronic%20devices%20(i.e.%20camera%2C%20phone%2C%20etc.)%20at%20the%20time%20of%20evidence%20collection%20by%20security%20staff%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20manual%20also%20provides%20for%20stringent%20punishment%20for%20%E2%80%9Call%20acts%20of%20violence%20and%20all%20forms%20of%20coercion%20such%20as%20gheraos%2C%20sit-ins%20or%20any%20variation%20of%20the%20same%20which%20disrupt%20the%20normal%20academic%20and%20administrative%20functioning%20of%20the%20University%20and%2For%20any%20act%20which%20incites%20or%20leads%20to%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20gheraos%2C%20laying%20siege%20or%20staging%20demonstrations%20around%20the%20residence%20of%20any%20member%20of%20the%20University%20Community%20or%20any%20other%20form%20of%20coercion%2C%20intimidation%20or%20disturbance%20of%20right%20to%20privacy%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20campus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20actions%20will%20attract%20one%20or%20two%20of%20the%20following%20punishments%20including%20a%20fine%20of%20upto%20Rs%2020%2C000%2C%20withdrawal%20of%20hostel%20facility%2C%20cancellation%20of%20admission%20or%20withdrawal%20of%20degree%20or%20denial%20of%20registration%20for%20a%20specified%20period%2C%20rustication%20and%20declaring%20out%20of%20bounds%20from%20entire%20JNU%20campus%20up%20to%20four%20semesters%2C%20expulsion%20from%20the%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEither%20one%20or%20two%20of%20these%20punishments%20will%20also%20be%20handed%20out%20for%20possession%20of%20illegal%20arms%2C%20any%20intimidation%20or%20insulting%20behaviour%20towards%20students%20or%20staff%2C%20wrongful%20confinement%20of%20staff%20or%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20states%20that%20the%20punishments%20may%20be%20applied%20for%20%E2%80%9Cany%20other%20act%20which%20may%20be%20considered%20by%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%20or%20any%20other%20competent%20authority%20to%20be%20an%20act%20of%20violation%20of%20discipline%20and%20conduct.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20also%20state%20that%20students%20may%20face%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%206%2C000%20and%2For%20may%20have%20to%20carry%20out%20JNU%20community%20service%20for%20%E2%80%9Corganising%20events%20such%20as%20freshers%E2%80%99%20welcome%20parties%2C%20farewells%20or%20DJ%20events%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20campus%20without%20prior%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAimed%20at%20stifling%20vibrant%20campus%20culture%3A%20JNUSU%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JNUSU%20(the%20students%E2%80%99%20body)%20of%20the%20campus%20has%20condemned%20the%20new%20rules%20and%20demanded%20that%20they%20be%20revoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JNUSU%20said%20that%20the%20rules%20were%20brought%20in%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20any%20discussion%20or%20deliberation%20with%20the%20stakeholders%20of%20the%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20manual%20grants%20unprecedented%20powers%20to%20the%20Chief%20Proctor%2C%20compromising%20the%20autonomy%20of%20the%20student%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20stringent%20measures%20outlined%20in%20the%20manual%20are%20aimed%20at%20stifling%20the%20vibrant%20campus%20culture%20that%20has%20defined%20JNU%20for%20decades.%20Such%20excessive%20regulations%20are%20intended%20to%20discourage%20open%20discussions%2C%20dissent%2C%20and%20intellectual%20exploration%2C%20which%20are%20fundamental%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20our%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JNUSU%20said%20that%20the%20manual%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20students%20are%20facing%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20academic%20and%20infrastructural%20issues%20in%20the%20campus%E2%80%9D%20including%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20journals%2C%20disrupted%20water%20supply%2C%20crumbling%20hostel%20buildings%2C%20delayed%20hostel%20admissions%2C%20and%20shortened%20semesters%2C%20among%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20repeated%20demands%20from%20the%20student%20community%2C%20the%20university%20administration%20has%20been%20unjustly%20delaying%20the%20conduct%20of%20student%20union%20elections%2C%20which%20has%20been%20stalled%20for%20four%20years%20now.%20The%20attack%20on%20the%20Student%20Union%20and%20student%20activism%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20very%20democratic%20ethos%20that%20has%20built%20the%20university%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20note%20in%20the%20foreword%20to%20the%20manual%20Chief%20Proctor%20Prof.%20N.%20Janardhana%20Raju%20said%20that%20the%20rules%20were%20brought%20in%20because%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cstrongly%20felt%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20existing%20disciplinary%20rules%20be%20reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20strongly%20felt%20to%20review%20the%20existing%20disciplinary%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20Office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Proctor%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20foreward%20note%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20no%20substantially%20approved%20rules%20and%20regulations%20on%20proper%20conduct%20and%20discipline%20of%20students%20by%20the%20Statutory%20Body%20(i.e.%20Executive%20Council)%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20in%20vogue.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20undertake%20a%20careful%20preparation%20of%20Chief%20Proctor%20Office%20(CPO)%20manual%20encompassing%20rules%20and%20regulations%20to%20be%20followed%20during%20the%20proctorial%20enquiry%20based%20on%20the%20experiences%20accumulated%20over%20the%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20reached%20out%20to%20JNU%20vice%20chancellor%20Santishree%20Dhulipudi%20Pandit%20for%20a%20comment.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20a%20response%20is%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702376112000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F06144304%2Fdu-protest.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjnu-institutes-new-rules-to-punish-protests-with-fines-rustication-from-campus%22%2C%22summary%2