0unaware%20of%20history.%20I%20cannot%20expect%20him%20to%20know%20history%2C%20he%20has%20the%20habit%20of%20rewriting%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20told%20reporters%20outside%20parliament%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20just%20a%20way%20of%20distracting%20people%20from%20real%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20great-grandson%20of%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20backed%20the%20Centre's%20move%20to%20scrap%20Article%20370%20and%20end%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20blamed%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20for%20%26quot%3Btwo%20major%20blunders%26quot%3B%20-%20declaring%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20a%20war%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20taking%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20to%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20no%20untimely%20ceasefire%20(during%20the%20war%20with%20Pakistan)%2C%20there%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20a%20PoK%20(Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir).%20Our%20country%20was%20winning%2C%20had%20he%20(Nehru)%20waited%20for%20two%20days%2C%20entire%20Kashmir%20would%20have%20been%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20say%20if%20not%20for%20Nehru%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20no%20Kashmir.%20People%20who%20know%20history%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20them%2C%20Hyderabad%20faced%20a%20bigger%20problem%2C%20did%20Nehru%20go%20there%3F%20Did%20Nehru%20go%20to%20Lakshadweep%2C%20Junagarh%20or%20Jodhpur%3F%20He%20only%20used%20to%20go%20to%20Kashmir%20and%20even%20there%20he%20left%20the%20job%20unfinished%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20order%20vindicated%20the%20government's%20stand%2C%20said%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20who%20was%20the%20one%20to%20announce%20in%202019%20the%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20bifurcation%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20move%20to%20mainstream%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir