-data-illegal-migrants-not-possible-14346-foreigners-deported-5-years-centre-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20came%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Faccurate-data-illegal-migrants-not-possible-14346-foreigners-deported-5-years-centre-supreme-court%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20inquiry%20into%20immigrants%20conferred%20Indian%20citizenship%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20Section%206A(2)%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%201955.%20The%20Court%20had%20sought%20these%20details%20while%20hearing%20a%20challenge%20to%20its%20validity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Section%206A%20people%20who%20entered%20India%20between%20January%201%2C%201966%2C%20and%20March%2025%2C%201971%2C%20and%20have%20been%20living%20in%20Assam%2C%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20register%20themselves%20as%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%206A%20of%20the%20Act%20was%20accepted%20by%20Parliament%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20memorandum%20of%20agreement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fassam-citizenship-case-sc-tells-union-govt-to-give-details-on-undocumented-immigrants-in-northeast%5C%22%3Epopularly%20known%20as%20the%20Assam%20Accord%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20signed%20in%201985%20between%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20anti-foreigner%20agitation%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20immigrants%20entering%20the%20state%20without%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20petitions%20have%20been%20filed%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20this%20provision%20and%20concerns%20that%20it%20has%20worsened%20the%20problem%20of%20illegal%20immigration%20in%20Assam%2C%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Faccurate-data-illegal-migrants-not-possible-14346-foreigners-deported-5-years-centre-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ereported%