%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20Is%20the%20Man%20the%20Moment%20Needs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12123038%2FGAG4iqtbcAAtrm1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20clarion%20call%20for%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%20The%20Congress%20had%20bet%20on%20these%20polls%2C%20expecting%20that%20a%20positive%20outcome%20would%20yield%20it%20greater%20bargaining%20power%20with%20other%20regional%20players%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20regional%20constituents%20of%20INDIA%20expressed%20their%20anguish%2C%20as%20the%20Congress%20had%20forced%20the%20idea%20of%20INDIA%20to%20take%20the%20backseat%2C%20after%20an%20enthusiastic%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20victories%20in%20the%20three%20heartland%20states%20have%20made%20one%20aspect%20of%20Indian%20elections%20clear.%20They%20have%20increasingly%20become%20bi-polar%20contests%2C%20and%20with%20a%20dominant%20BJP%20in%20pole%20position%2C%20the%20INDIA%20constituents%20will%20only%20end%20up%20undercutting%20each%20other%20if%20they%20prioritise%20their%20egos%20over%20their%20common%20concerns.%20The%20Congress%20and%20other%20anti-BJP%20forces%20appear%20to%20have%20stagnated%20at%20their%20traditional%20vote%20shares%2C%20with%20minor%20increases%20here%20and%20there.%20But%20those%20are%20only%20occasional%20and%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20factored%20in%20easily%2C%20given%20the%20drastic%20changes%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20have%20witnessed%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%20The%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20surging%20towards%20the%2050%25%20mark%20in%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20circumstances%2C%20INDIA%20needs%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20basics.%20It%20needs%20to%20project%20a%20dynamic%20collective%20leadership%2C%20chart%20an%20ideological%20narrative%20that%20clearly%20differentiates%20it%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20expand%20its%20social%20base.%20Given%20how%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20still%20fighting%20over%20territorial%20control%2C%20this%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20They%20have%20less%20than%20five%20months%20to%20face%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20which%20most%20probably%20will%20also%20be%20a%20period%20when%20the%20BJP%20goes%20into%20political%20overdrive.%20Yet%2C%20to%20come%20together%20as%20early%20as%20possible%20is%20the%20only%20option%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20PMO%20Has%20Morphed%20Into%20an%20Independent%20Executive%20Force%20%E2%80%93%20Where%20Is%20the%20Cabinet%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fpmo-modi-mallikarjun-kharge-book-excerpt%5C%22%3EThe%20PMO%20Has%20Morphed%20Into%20an%20Independent%20Executive%20Force%20%E2%80%93%20Where%20Is%20the%20Cabinet%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20INDIA%20leaders%20think%20that%20merely%20reaching%20a%20consensus%20on%20seat-sharing%20can%20trump%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20may%20be%20in%20for%20another%20unpleasant%20surprise.%20The%20recent%20polls%20showed%20that%20the%20single-biggest%20issue%20of%20a%20caste%20census%20that%20INDIA%20parties%20raised%20had%20barely%20any%20takers%20on%20the%20ground.%20This%20only%20implies%20that%20all%20INDIA%20constituents%20will%20have%20to%20work%20together%20to%20create%20a%20competitive%20political%20narrative%20around%20the%20demand.%20They%20have%20to%20channel%20their%20resources%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20message%20reaches%20the%20targets%20%E2%80%95%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20the%20Adivasis.%20And%20they%20have%20to%20walk%20this%20talk%20by%20taking%20radical%20and%20possibly%20risky%20decisions%20like%20promoting%20new%20leadership%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20sidelining%20leaders%20who%20have%20become%20liabilities%2C%20and%20drawing%20more%20candidates%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20require%20an%20unprecedented%20joint%20effort%20on%20their%20part%20to%20mobilise%20people%20and%20connect%20with%20them%2C%20even%20as%20they%20will%20need%20to%20bring%20order%20to%20their%20own%20houses.%20The%20leaders%20and%20workers%20of%20all%20INDIA%20constituents%20need%20to%20speak%20in%20one%20voice%2C%20avoid%20getting%20trapped%20in%20unnecessary%20controversies%2C%20and%20raise%20common%20issues%20aggressively%20for%20their%20supporters%20to%20rally%20around.%20Only%20then%20can%20they%20expect%20to%20have%20a%20shot%20at%20unseating%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20resentment%20among%20people%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20issues%20like%20price%20rise%2C%20unemployment%20and%20a%20general%20sense%20of%20alienation.%20But%20INDIA%20is%20far%20from%20being%20a%20credible%20alternative%20to%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20electorate%2C%20however%20hard%20one%20tries%20to%20look%20at%20it%20positively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Herculean%20challenge%20that%20INDIA%20faces%20at%20the%20moment%20can%20only%20be%20met%20by%20surefooted%20leaders.%20Since%20regional%20players%20in%20INDIA%20have%20already%20given%20the%20mantle%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20role%20of%20Mallikajrun%20Kharge%20will%20be%20decisive.%20In%20the%20short%20time%20that%20he%20has%20helmed%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20has%20shown%20enough%20signs%20that%20he%20could%20be%20the%20fulcrum%20that%20INDIA%20needs%2C%20as%20other%20big%20leaders%20like%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20and%20even%20Sharad%20Pawar%20will%20have%20to%20remain%20in%20their%20strongholds.%20Kharge%20has%20attempted%20to%20implement%20progressive%20decisions%20announced%20in%20the%20Udaipur%20Declaration%20of%202022%2C%20but%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20spend%20enough%20time%20at%20the%20top.%20He%20has%20also%20focussed%20his%20election%20speeches%20on%20issues%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20shown%20a%20strong%20commitment%20towards%20multiculturalism%2C%20although%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20received%20much%20support%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20regional%20satraps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22With%20Internal%20Democracy%20Taking%20Root%2C%20Congress%20Appears%20To%20Be%20Thriving%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finternal-democracy-congress-thriving%5C%22%3EWith%20Internal%20Democracy%20Taking%20Root%2C%20Congress%20Appears%20To%20Be%20Thriving%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20book%20on%20Kharge%20in%20New%20Delhi%20recently%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20MP%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Jha%20narrated%20from%20personal%20experience%20that%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20capacity%20to%20listen%20to%20others%20makes%20him%20fundamentally%20different%20from%20many%20other%20leaders.%20The%20Congress%20president%20has%20had%20a%20parallel%20life%20with%20the%20Indian%20republic%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20that%20reflects%20in%20his%20commitment%20to%20justice%2C%20freedom%20and%20equality.%20%E2%80%9CDr%20Ambedkar%20was%20guided%20by%20the%20idea%20of%20emancipation%20and%20Nehru%20stood%20for%20compassion%2C%20then%20Kharge%20is%20building%20a%20bridge%20between%20the%20two%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%E2%80%99s%20acceptability%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20makes%20him%20the%20ideal%20candidate%20to%20steer%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20Backed%20by%20decades%20of%20political%20experience%2C%20only%20he%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20pack%20an%20united%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702366256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12123038%2FGAG4iqtbcAAtrm1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-