ommittee%3A%20Kuki%20Groups%20Claim%20No%20Dialogue%20With%20Them%2C%20Deny%20Report%E2%80%99s%20Findings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20however%2C%20directed%20the%20petitioners%20%E2%80%93%20Yumlembam%20Surjit%20Singh%2C%20Keisham%20Arish%20and%20Laishram%20Momo%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20to%20approach%20the%20Gita%20Mittal%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20has%20already%20constituted%20a%20committee%20chaired%20by%20Justice%20(retired)%20Gita%20Mittal.%20It%E2%80%99s%20open%20to%20make%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20committee.%20At%20this%20stage%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20broad%20and%20general%20reliefs%20would%20not%20result%20in%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-entertain-pil-for-fresh-panel-of-experts-on-manipur-violence-724722-2023-12-11%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20instant%20petition%20in%20Public%20Interest%20is%20being%20filed%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20seeking%20directions%20to%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20to%20restore%20law%20and%20order%2C%20and%20peace%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Manipur%20and%20also%20to%20constitute%20an%20expert%20committee%20to%20prepare%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20suggest%20possible%20remedial%20measures.%20The%20present%20petition%20is%20being%20filed%20to%20protect%20and%20secure%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2021%2C%2014%20and%2019%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20already%20hearing%20petitions%20on%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20had%20established%20the%20Gita%20Mittal%20committee%20in%20August%20to%20assess%20the%20situation%20and%20suggest%20remedial%20measures.%20The%20committee%20had%20submitted%20its%20in