%20procedure%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263534%2Fanupath-tripathi-squid-game-netflix-facts-korean-drama-abdul-ali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20South%20Korea%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%202008%2C%20a%20nurse%20accidentally%20inserted%20a%20knife%20right%20through%20the%20heart.%20When%20I%20inquired%20later%2C%20she%20explained%20that%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20accurately%20gauge%20the%20depth.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20problems%20like%20this%2C%20SSI%20Mantra%202%20provides%20a%20better%20view%20of%20the%20organs%20as%20depth%20perception%20is%20crucial%20in%20surgery%20for%20bringing%20in%20instruments%20and%20supplies%2C%20avoiding%20accidents%2C%20and%20shortening%20the%20learning%20curve.%20Since%20its%20launch%20in%202022%2C%20the%20system%20has%20already%20assisted%20doctors%20in%20performing%20500%20successful%20surgeries%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20future%20plans%2C%20Dr%20Sudhir%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20developed%20numerous%20single-arm%20applications.%20Our%20approach%20involves%20smaller%20and%20lighter%20robotic%20arms%2C%20and%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20develop%20different%20types%20of%20arms%20that%20can%20perform%20different%20functions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20main%20aim%20is%20to%20decentralise%20excellence%20wherever%20possible%2C%20make%20the%20technology%20cheaper%20and%20easy%20to%20access%20so%20that%20we%20can%20reach%20every%20rural%20corner%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20their%20approach%20holistic%2C%20he%20opines%20that%20utilising%20technology%20is%20crucial%20for%20advancing%20medicine%20today.%20In%20many%20rural%20areas%2C%20the%20population%20remains%20underprivileged%20in%20terms%20of%20accessing%20the%20best%20possible%20medical%20care%2C%20often%20due%20to%20physicians%E2%80%99%20reluctance%20to%20go%20there%20for%20various%20reasons.%3